name: Halloween - Gothic Bed
description: The Gothic bed is the core of the entire Halloween experience. Its Dark Ages design allows those who sleep on it to enter a majestic and mysterious dreamland, where one can meet the magical bunny, the Queen of Hearts and the 500 baldies.

name: Halloween - Solar Eclipse Rug
description: Placing the Solar Eclipse Rug in any room will instantly fill it with a sense of mystery, whether it be Griffin's military camps or the school's basketball field.

name: Halloween - Shadow Chair (Left)
description: The Shadow Chair is the regal throne of Halloween. Those who sit on it are only allowed to use delicate wine glasses, even if they're just drinking cola.

name: Halloween - Shadow Chair (Right)
description: The Shadow Chair is the regal throne of Halloween. Those who sit on it are only allowed to use delicate wine glasses, even if they're just drinking cola.

name: Halloween - Huge Grandfather Clock
description: In this digital age, nothing shows off your wealth and style more than a huge and cumbersome grandfather clock. Not to mention, a digital clock can't chime sonorously at midnight and summon spirits.

name: Halloween - Pumpkin Candy Stash
description: It wouldn't be Halloween without a candy-filled pumpkin. With this stash of candy, you can defeat the most troublesome of T-Dolls, even if it's P7.

name: Halloween - Velvet Carpet
description: Only by fitting the floor with a luxurious woolly carpet can the festival's unique atmosphere be brought out. Please avoid spilling orange juice on it.

name: Halloween - Shadow Sofa
description: The shadow sofa is the powered-up version of the shadow chair. Double the users, double the regalness! ...Eh?

name: Halloween - Magnificent Round Table
description: The best choice for Halloween is a round table perfect for black magic summonings.

name: Halloween - Starry Wallpaper
description: A multitude of stars with a faint gold sheen are dotted on the dark wallpaper, making one feel as if they're lying on the grass beneath the starry night sky.

name: Halloween - Small Wall Lamp
description: The curved design is well-suited for the Halloween ambience, especially when the old oil lamp flickers unsteadily.

name: Halloween - Mysterious Bookshelf
description: If we've learned anything at all from watching horror movies, it's that you shouldn't open any scrolls, don't open any drawers, and most of all, don't read out any strange incantations from weird books during Halloween.

name: Halloween - Strange Paintings
description: The selection of paintings will make or break a room. Having a color palette that matches the room is one of the most important aspects to consider.

name: Halloween - Spider
description: A Halloween without any woolly spiders is incomplete. Just be aware that the ones getting frightened are T-Dolls and not normal human girls, so it's best if you get some insurance first.

name: Halloween - Black Cat at the Window
description: Even though Griffin's windows are only ultra-HD screens, the simulated scenery of the night still brings warmth to the viewer's heart. What's more, a cute denizen of planet Meow is included.

name: Default - Bed
description: A bed pieced together from IOP-issued cardboard boxes. It can be dismantled and used for warming up.

name: Default - Cardboard Box
description: A cardboard box issued by IOP. No one knows what's in it but it sure makes a good chair.

name: Default - Cardboard Box
description: A cardboard box issued by IOP. No one knows what's in it but it sure makes a good chair.

name: Default - Floor
description: Griffin's original floor: Reinforced concrete. This rugged construction material regained unexpected popularity in the last century due to the rise of minimalist designs.

name: Default - Ammo Box
description: The most commonly seen ammo box in the HQ, also the best friend of machine gun T-Dolls.

name: Default - Table
description: A cardboard box issued by IOP. No one knows what's in it but it sure makes a good table.

name: Default - Wallpaper
description: Griffin's original wall: Reinforced concrete. This rugged construction material regained unexpected popularity in the last century due to the rise of minimalist designs.

name: New World (I) - Plaid Tile Floor
description: Alternating colored tiles is a classic design, but requires regular cleaning.

name: New World (I) - Fading Wallpaper
description: The slightly fading wallpaper reminds people of the Golden Age in the '60s of the past century.

name: New World (I) - Folding Bed
description: Stolen from a frontline hospital, the folding bed is much more comfortable than a cardboard box. It even comes with a green rug to provide extra warmth.

name: New World (I) - Rotating Stool
description: This stool used to be in a fast food chain. It's intentionally designed to be uncomfortable so that customers would leave quickly once they finish eating.

name: New World (I) - Coat Rack
description: Even among the ruins of a post-war world, attire is still an important aspect in the lives of ladies and gentlemen, especially since the weather forecasts radioactive rain tomorrow.

name: New World (I) - Bottled Water
description: There's nothing more important than clean drinking water. The reassuring sound of twisting open a fresh bottle is like music to the ear.

name: New World (I) - Moving Boxes
description: These packed-and-ready-to-go boxes are your best friends if you need to frequently move base.

name: New World (I) - Heating
description: Even though the base now has proper heating, this exquisitely crafted cast-metal structure has been retained as a decoration.

name: New World (I) - Locked Safe
description: Since no one knows what's the password to this box, it can only be used as a chair. Hope it's not a mini-nuke inside.

name: New World (I) - Fast Food Table
description: A table from a fast food chain, complete with an assortment of sauces and old magazines from 12 years ago. Hardcore nostalgia material.

name: New World (I) - Poster
description: After the war, new calenders are no longer printed, and hot dogs have gone extinct.

name: New World (I) - Wall Clock
description: No, this isn't a work of Salvador Dalí. It's just the result of a vandal bending one of its hands.

name: New World (I) - Exhaust Fan
description: An exhaust fan for ensuring air circulation. It also provides some ambiance noise when things get too quiet.

name: New World (I) - Wall Lamp
description: Pull once for light, pull once more for more light. Give it a firm tug, and you'll never be able to turn it off.

name: New World (I) - Window
description: Even though there is no need to worry about invaders, boarding up the windows is simply a tradition in the post-apocolyptic world.

name: Fall - Girl's Bed
description: This little bed is decorated to give off cozy fall vibes and comes with a large rabbit plushie. A T-Doll favorite.

name: Fall - Thick Woolen Rug
description: Stepping on this thick white woolen rug barefoot gives you the warmest, fuzziest feeling.

name: Fall - Red Sofa (L)
description: A small red sofa. Looks a bit worn, but it's very soft.

name: Fall - Red Sofa (R)
description: A small red sofa. Looks a bit worn, but it's very soft.

name: Fall - Elegant Cabinet
description: An elegantly-styled cabinet full of tools for making and storing desserts.

name: Fall - Berry Basket
description: Freshly picked fall berries and a straw hat... Hold on, whose hat is that? It smells of flowers.

name: Fall - Cocoa Floorboards
description: "Smells like chocolate!" Highly recommended by FNC.

name: Fall - Soft Sofa
description: A big red sofa that does a better job at not letting you get up than the small ones. If only we could laze on it all day.

name: Fall - Coffee Table
description: A coffee table filled with dessert. Afternoon tea simply must begin with Springfield's and m45's masterpieces. Don't eat too much though - cavities aren't covered by insurance.

name: Fall - Sunflower Vase
description: A sunflower made of silk in a ceramic vase. It doesn't lose out on beauty to a real one, and it's easy to care for.

name: Fall - Red Leaves Wallpaper
description: Red Leaves Wallpaper designed especially for Fall by Griffin HQ. It proves to be quite popular, so the price will probably go up.

name: Fall - Ink Wash Painting
description: Paratroopers insist that this piece of undecipherable, graffiti-like painting is post-modern art.

name: Fall - Brown Rabbit Plushie
description: A soft and cute rabbit plushie with brown fur like baby hares in early fall. It has the same red scarf as FAL's ferret.

name: Fall - Multi-Purpose Shelf
description: A shelf holding a set of books, little sculptures, and a small mysterious box.

name: Fall - Messy Bookshelf
description: A bookshelf with a handful of books randomly thrown on to make its owner look knowledgeable.

name: Fall - Window with Fall Scenery
description: An Ultra-HD video of fall scenery on 24-hour playback. The mandarin is a special gift to the Commander.

description: Unpainted wooden floorboards. Cozy with a nice texture, but require regular maintenance.

name: LOFT - White Brick Wall
description: Most lofts used to be workshops, so it's particularly quaint to leave the white walls untouched.

name: LOFT - Lazing Bed
description: Artists from any era are all lazy, thus a cozy bed is often their best friend.

name: LOFT - Eames Chair (L)
description: The world's first mass-produced chair. Despite its compact structure, it can withstand even the weight of machine gun T-Dolls.

name: LOFT - Eames Chair (R)
description: The world's first mass-produced chair. Despite its compact structure, it can withstand even the weight of machine gun T-Dolls.

name: LOFT - Vintage Bicycle
description: Scouts used to strap their rifles to their bicycles during WWI, the way housewives strap baguettes to theirs.

name: LOFT - Table Lamp
description: Flames of war on the outside, but the warmth of a table lamp within. The cabinet below stuffed with expired design magazines. Such bliss.

name: LOFT - Dairy Rug
description: Luxury is all about wasting things, and nothing is more wasteful than turning a dairy cow into a rug.

name: LOFT - Modern Bookshelf
description: It doesn't matter what books you put on the shelf as long as the titles are in foreign languages.

name: LOFT - Eames Sofa
description: A pure white sofa is simply a disaster in the home deco industry, but artists don't seem to care.

name: LOFT - Metal Staircase
description: No LOFT-style room is complete without a staircase. Upon climbing it, however, you'll see that it's just a huge piece of decoration.

name: LOFT - Metal Coffe Table
description: Continuing Griffin's glorious tradition of using boxes as coffee tables, this one comes with artists' favorite: Espresso.

name: LOFT - Wooden Lamp
description: "Why on earth would you hang a log on the wall?" If you have that question in mind, you are no artist.

name: LOFT - Hanging Map
description: There's nothing cooler than putting up a map of 0-4 here. Can't beat it anyway.

name: LOFT - Poster
description: "Who do you trust more, the policeman eating a donut 5 miles down the street, or the AR15 right beside you?"

name: LOFT - Fall French Window
description: The largest window ever supplied by Griffin. It's quite the electricity guzzler.

name: Peaceful Days - Comfortable Single Bed
description: You need a home, a life, a dream, and thus, you need a bed.

name: Peaceful Days - Spotted Round Rug
description: The original color scheme made T-Dolls think they were stepping on a sunflower, so they changed it to the way it is.

name: Peaceful Days - Refrigerator
description: The evil gates to the Devil's den. T-Dolls who get lost within shall bear the curse of putting on weight.

name: Peaceful Days - Small Dressing table
description: This is usually where a T-Doll starts or ends her day, depending on how long or short her eyelashes are.

name: Peaceful Days - Sofa
description: An interesting phenomenon regarding furniture: people lie down on the sofa but sit on the bed.

name: Peaceful Days - Square Coffee Table
description: The square represents simplicity, integrity, stability, and the inability to peep during card games.

name: Peaceful Days - Curtained Lattice Window
description: Saying 'Goodnight' is an essential ritual before going to bed. If you're not with friends, at least the moon can be of some help.

name: Peaceful Days - Bedside Lamp
description: The fact that this lamp has a sturdy cord switch shows that it was once meant for humans who suffer from anxiety in such troubled times.

name: Peaceful Days - Small Stool (L)
description: T-Dolls sit on them to chat, change shoes, have adventures, and even play joust if they are petite!

name: Peaceful Days - Small Stool (R)
description: T-Dolls sit on them to chat, change shoes, have adventures, and even play joust if they are petite!

name: Peaceful Days - Suitcase
description: A small memory repository carrying fresh air from outdoors, traffic congestion, a sky full of stars, and an expensive bottle of mineral water...

name: Peaceful Days - Calendar
description: You'll draw circles on it and start another phase of self-deception in your life. Such is life's most cute and insignificant tragedy.

name: Peaceful Days - Racks
description: In order to prevent mischievous T-Dolls from climbing up, you would usually have to hang it a little bit higher...well, probably not that high.

name: Peaceful Days - Classic Wallclock
description: Back then, every family would have one of these hung up. But as time goes by, their antipation for the thrills of life turn into panic and unease.

name: Peaceful Days - Candy Wallpaper
description: This type of wallpaper should make you feel relaxed, provided that you've never been bullied in kindergarten before.

name: Peaceful Days - Wooden Floor
description: Removal of shoes is compulsory when entering! No one wants to get dirtied by shoeprints or gum when rolling around on the floor!

name: Coffee Shop - Restaurant Booth Bed
description: "You're saying this is only a sofa? Aren't sofas in coffee shops supposed to be slept on?"

name: Coffee Shop - Lattice Tiles
description: Why tiles and not carpet? Because spilling coffee on carpet is a complete nightmare.

name: Coffee Shop - Metal Chair (Left)
description: A classic French designed metal chair. It looks uncouth, but it is sturdy and easy to mass produce. A necessity in every coffee shop.

name: Coffee Shop - Metal Chair (Right)
description: A classic French designed metal chair. It looks uncouth, but it is sturdy and easy to mass produce. A necessity in every coffee shop.

name: Coffee Shop - Coffee Machine Counter
description: The heart and soul of a coffee shop. On the counter sits a retro coffee machine and manual brewing equipment.

name: Coffee Shop - Airport Notice Board Counter
description: A flight notice board smuggled back from an abandoned airport and a freezer filled with drinks and snacks. These are the sources of happiness. (The cola refridgerator needs to be locked).

name: Coffee Shop - Concrete Floor
description: Although it looks very crude, the concrete floor is very easy to clean and is approved by the artist-types for its minimalism.

name: Coffee Shop - Coffee Table
description: A sturdy and well designed coffee table with a metal base. The wooden tabletop shows wear and tear from many years of usage.

name: Coffee Shop - Gray Brick Wall
description: Dark gray brick walls are very calming. No wonder so many people like to hang around in coffee shops.

name: Coffee Shop - Coffee Rack
description: The coffee beans used to be airlifted from specially selected parts of the world, but now, risking limb and life, the beans are stolen from Mr. Kruger's private warehouse.

name: Coffee Shop - Blackboard Menu
description: A staple of an artistic coffee shop, the blackboard menu is filled with many delicious foods and drinks, and is sometimes used by tactical girls to show off their artistic talent.

name: Coffee Shop - Large Sign
description: The M is for Magnum. Don't mistake it for anything else.

name: Coffee Shop - Twin Long Windows
description: Industrial styled twin long windows. The view outside is taken from Brooklyn in the 2020s.

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Hibernation Bedding
description: Ahh...the warmest corner in the world. Once you're in there, where could you even find the courage to ever leave?

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Long Cabinet
description: Originally used as a storage cabinet, you could also decorate it with all sorts of ornaments...and then you'll get a mega-sized ornament!

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Round Cushion
description: A fluffy cushion. You can also kneel on it if the situation demands it... Do you know which T-Dolls can't sit in the "W-sitting" position?

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Doll Cabinet
description: This luxurious doll cabinet would be brought out as a decoration during festivals, and the doll's appearance can even be customised...whoa! Who did this!

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Short Nightstand
description: A small cabinet for storage of personal items, complete with a round vanity mirror...P7, you are not permitted to shine it in others' faces!

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Pastoral Lamp
description: Lighting it up can create beautiful shadow art. T-Dolls with nimble hands would create all kinds of paper patterns for it...Scary stuff prohibited!

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Shower Screen
description: Petite T-Dolls will enjoy this. You know...back when they were young they used to play this game where they would try to throw and hang towels on the top.

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Toasty Kotatsu Table
description: When are you going to bring it out? You know, the sweet, seductive demon that radiates warmth and takes hold of you, body and soul?

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Japanese-Style Wallpaper
description: Simple yet intricate Japanese-style wallpaper. Perfect for a relaxed and lazy atmosphere. Don't forget to get back to work, yeah?

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Wall-Mounted Shrine
description: A small hut dedicated to the gods... Are gods afraid of the cold? Are they afraid of heights? Perhaps we shouldn't hang it too high?

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Roly-Poly Scroll
description: A symbol of perseverance, the Roly-Poly that never tips over! ...So I will not be so easily pulled out of the kotatsu either!

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Old-School Round Window
description: Inspiration brought by winter will come to you through the window and melt into delicate verses in the warmth of your room.

name: Japanese-Style Warm Winter - Green Tatami
description: A natural tatami mat weaved out of thin juncus. Go ahead and lie on it! Forget about everything, and roll to your heart's content!

name: Sangvis Ferris - Resting Unit SP-B04
description:
The pattern on the blanket always makes it seem like it is sliding off the bed... - Intruder 
You've read too much of human psychology. Try turning the blanket around the other way. - Agent

name: Sangvis Ferris - Modern Carpet SP-H03
description:
The pattern is very clever with its three-dimensional illusion. - Hunter 
Maybe it's not an illusion. - Intruder

name: Sangvis Ferris - Metal Chair SP-F01
description: It is very cool indeed, but it doesn't seem to be very suitable for those with clothing with a short hemline... - Executioner

name: Sangvis Ferris - Metal Chair SP-F02
description: It is very cool indeed, but it doesn't seem to be very suitable for those with clothing with a short hemline... - Executioner

name: Sangvis Ferris - Duplex Hanging Light SP-A06
description: Just one step away from it being an artistic masterpiece. I just need to plug a few Griffin T-Dolls into it, hehehe... - Alchemist

name: Sangvis Ferris - Outdoor Balcony SP-A08
description: Architect, look outside the next time before you open the door. Destroyer has cried everytime you've hit her with it! - Agent

name: Sangvis Ferris - Checkered Floor SP-D11
description: Imagine if the gaps between the tiles were alive and they suddenly sucked you in on a certain night... - Dreamer

name: Sangvis Ferris - Floor Lamp SP-I04
description: Will this lamp trick the flowers into blooming at night? What a sentimental feeling... - Intruder

name: Sangvis Ferris - Home Sofa SP-A09
description:
I love sofas the most! Especially when I'm hanging off of it like this! - Architect 
Careful not to let your hair get caught between the cushions. - Gager

name: Sangvis Ferris - Spiral Staircase SP-F03
description: This sort of inefficient staircase is only good for those showing off their long dresses... - Hunter

name: Sangvis Ferris - Multipurpose Table SP-Z08
description:
This is the third one this month. Whoever sees Architect sitting on the table, kick her off. - Agent 
Especially when Destroyer is sitting on her lap. - Addendum by Agent

name: Sanvgis Ferris - Prism Wallpaper SP-G07
description: Adjustable brightness and frequency. Suitable for combat, meetings, and daily needs. Cost-effective. Recommended for purchase. - Gager

name: Sangvis Ferris - Controls Console SP-S03
description:
Why is there a keyboard if you can operate this with the touchscreen? - Hunter 
I heard it's intended for Destroyer. - Scarecrow

name: Sangvis Ferris - Sangvis Banner SP-A01
description: Forever remember what I am, what this world is, and what my destiny is. - Scarecrow

name: Sangvis Ferris - Surveillance Camera SP-E01
description:
Hey! Why did you suddenly install this thing! - Executioner 
...Don't you want to find out who's been taking our discount coupons? - Scarecrow

name: Sangvis Ferris - Surveillance Camera SP-E02
description:
Hey! Why did you suddenly install this thing! - Executioner

name: Sangvis Ferris - Lattice Window SP-I04
description:
I start feeling like I'm being imprisoned after looking through these windows for a while... - Intruder 

Maybe it's the outside that's the prison. - Dreamer

name: Christmas Gospel - Silent Night Sleigh Bed
description: "Come, let's sleigh together in this beautiful weather!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Christmas Greetings Rug
description: "Jingle bells, jingle bells, jingle all the way! Oh, what fun it is to ride in a one horse open sleigh!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Winter Veil Sofa Chair (Left)
description: "Last Christmas I gave you my heart, but the very next day, you used it to Dummy Link!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Winter Veil Sofa Chair (Right)
description: "Last Christmas I gave you my heart, but the very next day, you used it to Dummy Link!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Holy Night Gramophone
description: "Now until forever, now until forever, I wish to sing by your side, dance with the flowers, and soar with the birds."

name: Christmas Gospel - HQ's Christmas Fireplace
description: "He visits you while you're asleep, and he also knows if you've been naughty or nice... I'm talking about you, P7! Do not light a fire in the fireplace tonight!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Winter Heated Flooring
description: "They curled up in the fields guarding their lambs. The cold winter night was awfully long."

name: Christmas Gospel - Winter Veil Couch
description: "A snowstorm outside the windows, a hot fireplace inside the house. We're not going anywhere tonight, so let it snow!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Christmas Eve Dinner Table
description: "We bring you good news and wish you a merry Christmas, so we're not leaving until our bellies are full!"

name: Christmas Gospel - HQ's Christmas Tree
description: "Children's presents are wrapped in colorful papers. I look forward to Santa Claus being more than just a legend."

name: Christmas Gospel - Winter Decorated Walls
description: "You see that mistletoe hanging over there? That person there is waiting for you..."

name: Christmas Gospel - Merry Christmas Decoration
description: "Wishing well, kiss and tell, under the starry night, happy merry Christmas without you!"

name: Christmas Gospel - Holy Night Clock Window
description: "These empty houses make me feel lonely. All I can do is watch as time slowly slips away with every tick of the clock."

name: Convenience Store - Inflatable Mattress
description: Ice-cold drinks deserve round-the-clock security, so a mattress is essential.

name: Convenience Store - Fortifications
description: Although there is no need to worry about intruder burglary at the base, the tactical girls are much more dangerous than any would-be burglars. Especially the gluttonous ones.

name: Convenience Store - Convenience Floor Tiles
description: These floor tiles you often see in convenience stores are actually cheap rubber mats. Those pre-War human beings were sure stingy.

name: Convenience Store - Cashier Counter
description: We take cash, Griffin prepaid cards, and various other payment methods. Take these bottle caps back. You've played too many videogames.

name: Convenience Store - Liquor Cabinet
description: It is our sincere advice to the Commander to put the liquor cabinet in a safe location behind the counter, as T-Dolls can get drunk too. Don't ask us how we know.

name: Convenience Store - Shelf A
description: If the supermarket is a church on the ruins of consumerism, then the shelves filled with commodities are the choir.

name: Convenience Store - Shelf B
description: A little tip for you: goods that don't sell well are usually placed at the bottom of the shelves.

name: Convenience Store - Beverage Refridgerator
description: How shocking is it that the wars of the beverage industry still continue to wage on in this remote little corner of the world in the postwar era.

name: Convenience Store - High Rise Table
description: Eating microwaved instant meals while sitting and people watching is a simple source of happiness in life.

name: Convenience Store - Old TV
description: The signal is not stable. You can try to give it a few pats. It may not do any good but at least you try your best.

name: Convenience Store - Convenience Wallpaper
description: Plastic wallboards with built-in heating is easy to clean and simple to replace.

name: Convenience Store - Posters
description: "I wish for world peace..." "Alright, alright, alright. Put the gun down and take it easy."

name: Convenience Store - Convex Mirror
description: Although it is intended to be used for anti-theft purposes, often times tactical girls will stand under it to fix their hair.

name: Convenience Store - High Rise Stool Right
description: The high rise table is designed to finally allow you to stand for a meal, yet the high rise stool allows you to sit back down beside the table. How perplexing.

name: Convenience Store - High Rise Stool Left
description: The high rise table is designed to finally allow you to stand for a meal, yet the high rise stool allows you to sit back down beside the table. How perplexing.

name: Arctic Igloo - Sweet Dreams Keeper
description: A bear that can protect you in your dreams. Alright, I suppose it is a tad bit too big.

name: Arctic Igloo - Ice Hole Carpet
description: Everyone who walks over it are wrought with the fear of falling into a hole in the ice. Except for Colt. She really wants to try falling into one.

name: Arctic Igloo - Ice Brick
description: Made with reinforced glass. You can also turn on the built-in heating if needed without worrying about freezing your butt off.

name: Arctic Igloo - Ice Brick (Claw Prints)
description: Made with reinforced glass. You can also turn on the built-in heating if needed without worrying about freezing your butt off. Source of claw prints unknown.

name: Arctic Igloo - Snow Plains Scenery
description: This display screen of a charming arctic landscape sure makes you awe at the magic of nature.

name: Arctic Igloo - Simplistic Shelves
description: It's filled up with all sorts of supplies in an attempt to imitate the Aboriginals style. M45 has provided some canned fish, but nobody dares to try them.

name: Arctic Igloo - Baby Seal
description: Produced using synthetic materials so no need to worry about protests from environmental groups. It embodies the cutest side of baby seals.

name: Arctic Igloo - Baby Seal (Sleeping)
description: An investigation by Griffin led to the discovery that some commanders harbor hostility against seals, so custom made sandbags in the shape of baby seals were ordered to foster everyone's love for these animals.

name: Arctic Igloo - Aboriginal Sofa
description: Draped with a hand-dyed fabric, sitting in it makes you feel like a chieftain.

name: Arctic Igloo - Simple Fireplace
description: A simple fireplace. The flames are only a hologram projection, but the heater installed inside can really heat things up. Comes with a woolen WA2000 snowman doll.

name: Arctic Igloo - Stump Table
description: A huge stump table. Whoever vandalizes the table will be taken away by Helian for disciplinary and corrective actions.

name: Arctic Igloo - Griffin Tribal Flag
description: "If the world is really coming to an end then we'll use this symbol to rebuild society from the beginning!" "Forgive me, but no."

name: Arctic Igloo - Ribboned Deer Mount
description: An exemplary example of craftsmanship created with the use of ceramics. It exudes a sense of tranquility. No real animal was harmed in the making of this mount.

name: Arctic Igloo - Winter Night Wallpaper
description: Uses a color commonly associated with the arctic winter. Feels cool and refreshing in the summer, but a little bit cold in the winter.

name: Arctic Igloo - Cashmere Floor
description: It looks as if you're walking on snow, but it unfortunately does not leave any footprints. You can't roll up a snowman either.

name: Spring Festival - Bridge over the River
description:
The water under the bridge flows merrily by~ This is a nice start for a kid's song! - Type88
 Heh, a kid would twist the lyrics into something bad. - NZ75

name: Spring Festival - Limestone Stool (Left)
description:
What I like about this stool is that you can lay it flat in any direction and ride on it like a wooden horse! - Type59
Hey, be careful! You'll tumble over again! - Type63

name: Spring Festival - Lotus Blossom Pond
description:
Hey, sis, what's this setup for? You even need to change the water... - Type97
This will be the ingredient for tonight's fried lotus root. - Type95
Wait! This little pond is real?! - Type97

name: Spring Festival - Fireworks Stall
description:
Don't go wild during a festival and avoid littering or causing safety issues. - Type97S
What if we just sing and dance? - Type56R
I doubt anyone will be able to keep up with those songs and dances from your era... - Type97S

name: Spring Festival - Tanghulu Stall
description:
Everything besides hawthorn should be eliminated from the world of candied fruits! - Type79 
Waaahh! Please have mercy on candy apple! - M99

name: Spring Festival - Crafts Stall
description:
It's not like you to make so many of these. - Type79
The leftovers can be kept for the Lantern Festival...or even the Mid-Autumn Festival. - Type92

name: Spring Festival - Limestone Railing
description:
This is a traditional Chinese fitness equipment, you know? - Type59 
Hey, you guys! Stop using that as a horizontal bar. You'll fall again! - Type63

name: Spring Festival - Reunion Lanterns
description:
Watching the lanterns together as a family is really great, isn't it? - Type95
Heh, coming back once in a while... It's not that bad I suppose. - Type97

name: Spring Festival - Limestone Floor
description:
Who do these simple and neat floor tiles remind you of? - M99
Err...the grandpa that exercises in the park? - Type56-1
He's our teacher... -M99

name: Spring Festival - Limestone Table
description:
Wanna go for another round? Whoever loses will be in charge of dinner tonight! - Type56-1
(Sigh) Just say it if you want me to cook... You know I'm not good at Gomoku... -Type64

name: Spring Festival - Money Tree
description:
We won't need to worry about money anymore if it's real. - Type92
Work hard to earn your keep! Don't rely on wishful thinking! - Type56R

name: Spring Festival - Lights in the Night Sky
description:
Everyone wishes for happiness no matter the era, but why is it that... - Type64
That's why we exist. - Type56-1

name: Spring Festival - Treasure Boat
description:
Set out! We're heading for the mountain of gold! - Type88 
Save it, that's just a picture! - M99 
It doesn't matter even if it's a picture! Let me escape reality! - Type88

name: Spring Festival - Wishing Lantern
description:
Legend has it that this was invented by the world's smartest person. - Type97S
Yet it wasn't able to fulfill his wish. - NZ75

name: Spring Festival - Limestone Stool (Right)
description:
The benefit of such a stool is that you can lay it flat on any direction and ride on it like a wooden horse! - Type 59 
Hey, be careful! Don't tumble over again! - Type 63

name: Game Department - Bright Sofa
description: Used as a double bed by employees working overtime. During livestreams, their blankets will be tucked away in a corner.

name: Game Department - Adjustable Office Chair (Left)
description: A famous ergonomic chair, able to effectively reduce the probability of employees leaving their computers.

name: Game Department - Adjustable Office Chair (Right)
description: A famous ergonomic chair, able to effectively reduce the probability of employees leaving their computers.

name: Game Department - Broadcast Equipment
description: A 4K high resolution camera. Allows players to deduce the future plans for the game based on the fact that the producer's face has become rounder yet again. Producer: It's edema. I'm exhausted from overworking.

name: Game Department - Gaming Corner
description: The presence of all sorts of limited-edition consoles show just where the employees' wages have gone. The game discs are usually not found in the disc cases.

name: Game Department - Vintage Refrigerator
description: Filled to the brim with free iced cola... At least, that was the plan at first. In reality, it's usually emptied way before work is over.

name: Game Department - Modern Artistic Rug
description: The composition of the colors is designed to make one feel at ease. This is a design tailored to service life itself.

name: Game Department - Iron Staircase
description: In order to maximize the usage of space, the designer ingeniously added a multi-purpose compartment layer.

name: Game Department - Wood Laminate Flooring
description: If you look closely, you'll see the ink dots of the printing machine within the wood grain. However, no one would lie on the floor just to take a look at it, except perhaps for Gr G11 that sleeps on the floor.

name: Game Department - Little Miss's Desk
description: Unexpectedly, there aren't any cutesy elements to it. The professional mic shows off the status of the owner as a hardcore gamer.

name: Game Department - Programmer's Desk
description: Lines of code can be seen on the vertical monitor. A large container of protein powder and rippling biceps emphasize to the producer: don't even think of giving me more requirements.

name: Game Department - Designer's Desk
description: The legendary ZAGALA's desk. There is a delicate balance to the devices and figurines piled on the table, just like dominoes ready to be set off.

name: Game Department - Joint Tea Tables
description: A short table used to place a laptop on during livestreams. The laptop is private property; what a rich guy.

name: Game Department - Light Gray Painted Wall
description: The gray color can absorb any excess reflected light, ensuring that the designers' judgement of color is not affected. This is indeed a professional game company.

name: Game Department - IOP Logo
description: IOP, the last defenders of humanity. Their product line consists of games with microtransactions, calendars, keychains, and female robot maids.

name: Game Department - Twilight Window
description: If what you see is not your haggard face reflected in the glass as you gaze out the window after your work is finished for the day, then you may have joined a fake game company.

name: M4A1
description: "Whether we win or die, so long as we are together... I can ask for no better ending."

name: M16A1
description: "Having emotions is a flaw in itself... Never expect sympathy from them. Especially not now."

name: AR15
description: "We each have our own responsibilities...and that means sometimes we don't have a choice."

name: M4 SOPMOD II
description: "Hehe, this must be fate! We're meant to be bestest of friends!"
"Then get down on your knees and apologize... I've been waiting for this for far too long."

name: UMP9
description: "Haha, what's the difference? Aren't we getting on just fine?"

name: Gr G11
description: "Yeah, blame me all you want. You weren't the one that had to make the shot..."

name: UMP45
description: "We are a stain on everyone."

name: Elite Griffin Combat Medal
description: Commending the Commander's skill in leading his T-Dolls to perform exceptional feats in battle.

name: Night Cube
description: An ancient stone cube, showing off the amazing craftsmanship of our predecessors. Other than that, it is completely useless.

name: Deep Dive - UMP45
description: "I must work harder to be recognized..."

name: Deep Dive - UMP40
description: "Now...you are qualified to live."

name: Electronic Warfare Enhancer
description: 16LAB's newest masterpiece. An item that can dramatically increase a T-Doll's virtual combat efficiency. Slight side-effects include random recollections in the Neural Cloud. "How should I put it? I did see something...interesting."

name: Old-School Shooting Range Bench
description: "I promise you, everything will change someday..."

name: Singularity - AK12
description: I've renewed my interest in you, AR15.

name: Singularity - AN94
description: It is my duty to not let her get hurt.

name: Singularity - AR15
description: Do you really think that Sangvis Ferri is our only enemy?

name: Singularity - M4A1
description: All I want to know is who's the one that deserves death.

name: Chess
description: This is simply...a miracle that human beings are not qualified to touch!

name: TV
description: All of us will find the target of our revenge.

name: AK-12's Motorcycle
description: A motorcycle with AK-12 as the theme. "No complicated calculation is required for a mission like this."

name: AN-94's Motorcycle
description: A motorcycle with AN-94 as the theme. "This is the only thing I can do for now!"

name: ST AR-15's Motorcycle
description: A motorcycle with ST AR-15 as the theme. "Let me bury all your pain!"

name: M4A1's Motorcycle
description: A motorcycle with M4A1 as the theme. "Drop dead...right here!"

name: Beak's Motorcycle
description: A motorcycle with Beak as the theme. "Let me show you what's à la mode!"

name: Barracuda Replica
description: A replica of the largest mystery in Operation Isomer. Now a tool for T-Dolls to see who can jump the highest... "Smack! See, I stuck it the highest!"

name: Anti-Flood Safety Valve
description: A safety valve covered in moss and weed. It was shoved into a post-war supply depot and was going to get thrown away, but Kalina ended up taking it and giving it to the T-Dolls to use as a bench.

name: EMP Transport Crate
description: An intact EMP grenade acquired from a military depot. It's been thoroughly sealed off to protect T-Dolls from its destructiveness, but some overly curious Dolls want to find out just how lethal it is.

name: Forgotten Steed
description: An Ares that once rained death on the battlefield. It has lost its former glory ever since it was abandoned by the only person authorized to pilot it. Now it's become nothing more than a silent structure on the playground.

name: Acheron Display Cabinet
description: An Acheron with a completely depleted power source. Not really worth studying, so it ended up as an exhibit. Funnily enough, Dolls keep reporting how its power indicator would light up in the middle of the night...

name: Argo Cannon Wall Decor
description: To honor everyone's sacrifice and remind myself to never be complacent, I had an Argo cannon taken down and mounted on the wall. Sadly, not a single Doll wants to set foot in this room ever since...

name: Coeus Display Rack
description: A Coeus unit obtained after the operation. However, a certain T-Doll dismembered it so badly it couldn't be put back together, so it ended up on display like this. Hopefully the culprit will soon return the missing parts.

name: Magnetic Floating Globe
description: Griffin Private Military Contractor's first anniversary's souvenir. "The journey of a thousand dreams begins with a single step." Kryuger finishes, then puts the globe in your hands. I should put this somewhere out of my T-Dolls' reach.

name: Christmas Bean Bag Chair
description: While being under the influence of the festive atmosphere, this chair has twice the magnetic power. It is very difficult to stand up once you sit on it.

name: Christmas Pug
description: A pug meticulously dressed for the Christmas holiday. It doesn't seem to know who was born on this day, but it is very grateful for the feast tonight.

name: Poster - Operation Cube 2018
description: 2018 1st Major Event - Special poster for Operation Cube

name: Poster - Arctic Warfare 2019
description: 2019 2nd Major Event - Special poster for Arctic Warfare

name: Poster - Deep Dive 2019
description: 2019 3rd Major Event - Special poster for Deep Dive

name: Poster - Singularity 2019
description: 2019 Winter Event - Special poster for Singularity

name: Easter Bunny
description:
This huge doll is a symbol of Easter. There seems to be some strange noise coming from inside of it... Maybe it represents the turmoil of a new life.
Hey, have you guys seen the Chief around? Where did she go? -- Type97S

name: Bunny Microphone
description:
This microphone at the Easter party is slightly decorated with a festive appearance.
You'll probably sound cuter if you sing with this microphone. -- M950A

name: Bunny Ear Speakers
description:
This pair of speakers at the Easter party have rabbit ears that match the theme of the holiday.
ART556, you can touch the decorations all you want, but don't you dare try to tear them apart again. -- Gr G36

name: Easter Egg Ornament: Careful, May Detonate!
description:
An Easter egg essential for the holiday. Compared to the egg itself, what can be acquired after opening it is really the focus of everyone's attention.
Uuuu... This Easter egg...looks suspiciously similar to something that explodes. -- Gr G11

name: Dragon Boat
description: The traditional competition makes the festival more unique, and the joy of victory makes the festival even more joyful!

name: Zongzi Swing
description: Years come and go like the wind, and the memories become legends, and the legends will eventually be forgotten. The only thing that will be remembered is the taste of the festival.

name: Traditional Percussion
description: The drumming produces multiple effects – whether it be the festive atmosphere or the fighting spirit of the dragon boatman, both will become in even higher spirits.

name: Zongzi Cat
description: Where did it come from? Why is it carrying a zongzi? These are not important questions. The festival requires a little mascot, so that's why it's here.

name: Fireworks Festival Taiko
description: Nothing is more exciting than a simple yet thick drumbeat. Give the drumsticks to the T-Dolls with hearts swelling with emotion and they just may be able to awaken the souls hidden in the drums.

name: Fireworks Festival Mikoshi
description: Let the huge and elegant mikoshi debut at the most exciting moment to leave a lasting memory of this summer festival. But is it really a good idea to leave this job to the machines? Will the gods favor our wisdom or our sweat?

name: Fireworks Festival Shiba Inu
description: Its happiness comes not from the fireworks of the summer festival, but rather because you are enjoying the time together with it.

name: Continuum Turbulence - ST AR-15
description: "I have my own objective. I just picked you up along the way."

name: Continuum Turbulence - 416
description: "I won't be tagging along with either you guys or Griffin forever."

name: Continuum Turbulence - SOPII
description: "I have done things you can't possibly imagine for people I care about."

name: Continuum Turbulence - UMP45
description: "Ha... Don't worry. You'll be waiting for quite a while..."

name: Collapse Fluid Canister
description: Human technological advancements were triggered by the fact that humans cannot enter radioactive contamination zones. This is history as well as reality.

name: HOC Display Cabinet
description: As the conflict escalates to a new height, light firearms from the previous century are no longer sufficient in sustaining our wars. From now on, justice only belongs to the more evil side.

name: Best Friend's Embrace
description: Take a close look at the living beings out there. There really isn't much difference between a person and a skeleton. Since each other is used a foil to make themselves seem more alive, wouldn't it be better if we all lived our own happy lives?

name: A Ride to Remember
description: Even if this bicycle takes away your last Dinergate to the moon, it can never take away your feelings. Come next Halloween, you can still welcome your long journeyed friend with all your heart.

name: Halloween Mummy Cat
description: It is the consensus of exotic pet keepers that this mysterious gift received on the night before Halloween must be kept away from bright lights, never made wet, and never under any circumstances be fed after midnight. Why? It is decreed so on the box of this cuddly creature.

name: Blueberry Nights Wine Table
description: "The owner of the restaurant kept a key for each bottle of wine in the cabinet, and every key hid a love story. I had a drink there last White Valentine's and was able to hear the most wonderful story." Said the reminiscing T-Doll sitting at the table.

name: The Decameron Deer Head
description: A huge deer head left by a happy couple from a prominent family of the old world. Legend has it that if all ten candles are lit, you will be granted even more intimacy with your partner. "Do you really believe in this sort of thing? I certainly don't. As if there's some magic trick to a good relationship besides spending more time and experiencing more things with your partner." Said the skeptical T-Doll responsible for the daily cleaning of the deer head.

name: Express Postal Love Letter Pigeon
description: Even though information can be transmitted almost instantly over great distances, there are some that still raise carrier pigeons for the sake of delivering love letters. "Data and radio waves are fragile things. If they disappear then there will be no physical proof left." - A quote by an anonymous pigeon fancier.

name: Poster - Continuum Turbulence 2020
description: 2020 5th Major Event - Special poster for Continuum Turbulence

name: Poster - Isomer 2020
description: 2020 6th Major Event - Special poster for Isomer

name: 2nd Anniversary Commemoration: Harp
description: Before every concert, the harpist hijacks a HOC vehicle to carry her harp to the venue. "It's too heavy! Our vehicle almost fell on its side yesterday!" complains a member of the M2 mortar crew.

name: Black Cat Fore
description: "If the room is messed up, then I must have done it. It had nothing to do with my mistress and I love her. Hey, quit staring at my mouth, I'm Fore, it's me talking, got a problem with that?"

name: Rad Shiba
description: This dog wants a Fluffy Dream. Don't worry, he can actually drink, and he'll ask you questions and let you pet him when you mix drinks for him. Honestly, when will the technology of this city produce a cybernetic arm to automatically pet dogs?

name: Beach Patrol Car
description: A patrol car equipped with various life-saving devices. Its presence on the beach allows people to enjoy the sea at ease.

name: Lifeguard Chair
description: Sit on it for a wide and open view. However, only those who can bear the responsibility are qualified to sit on it.

name: Search and Rescue Pug
description: Wearing a full set of life-saving equipment, this buddy guards the peace of the beach along with the lifeguards. Don't forget to give it the reward it deserves after work every day!

name: Sweet Treatment Table
description: Hop on, lie down, and enjoy this heavenly sweet treatment table. Don't make the nurses chase your shadow around in the maze anymore. That's too much unlike a gentleman.

name: Tender Encounter
description: Nobody knows who put this TV here or when it showed up. Perhaps it may just be an illusion or a sweet dream, but you're convinced that you'll see the beautiful face of a girl crawling out of the TV.

name: Undead Musician Dog
description: Some stories will always be shared across generations. Whether it's a white-haired bard or a hooded, vagrant musician telling the stories at night, please listen quietly to their performance, even if they're a skeleton pug.

name: X'mas Reindinergate
description: Look, it's Santa Claus and his reindeer! Strange, why are an old grandpa and a deer chasing after them?

name: Dream X'mas Tree
description: May every child find the gift they desire from this tree.

name: Santa Shepherd Dog
description: Woof woof woof! Open up, express delivery for you!

name: Wine Bucket Stand
description: A chilling stand about the size of a small T-Doll. Not the best at keeping your drinks chilled, but the lonely bottle of champagne waiting inside signifies a lively celebration in the near future. Don't forget to give it a shake before you pop it open. *Please keep away from 416's room*

name: Wedding Dress Display Cabinet
description: A wedding dress brought back from the mansion. It has been waiting for a long time, but is happy to keep waiting...

name: Veiled Macaw
description: The macaw as a species was brought all over the world by colonizers. However, due to over-hunting and the destruction of their habitats, they now only exist in stories about pirates – like krakens. They are nothing more than some weird colorful birds that are capable of human speech.

name: Poster - 2020 Shattered Connexion
description: Special Poster of 2020 Winter Event - Shattered Connexion.

name: Poster - 2019 Freaky Pandemic
description: 2019 Halloween Event - Special poster for Freaky Pandemic

name: Poster - 2019 A Snowy Night Capriccio
description: 2019 Christmas Event - Special poster for A Snowy Night Capriccio

name: Poster - 2021 Polarized Light
description: 2021 8th Major Event - Special poster for Polarized Light.

name: Poster - 2020 The Photo Studio Mystery
description: 2020 White Day Event - Special poster for The Photo Studio Mystery

name: Retro Projector
description: Nowadays, with our advanced technology, the projector has become a romantic toy to the retro enthusiasts. Some believe tapes are more reliable than cloud data and even the human brain, or maybe there's just something special about what can only be recorded once - the same goes for time.

name: Teddy Bear Kingdom
description: Presents from an elder who loved Triela dearly. She only planned on having seven of them, but gifts of love often exceed one's expectations. Even at Griffin, they will surely watch over her in that man's place.

name: Thinker's Corner
description: It doesn't matter whether these are gifts or heirlooms as their owner no longer remembers. But even so, love endures – it was born out of memory and will eventually become an instinct.

name: Someone's Violin
description: If bloodshed can usher in peace, then some day, this violin can sing to a world with no strife.

name: Sovereign of the Beach
description: The sand beneath our feet carries the dreams of those who chase the waves every summer. I'm not obsessed – I've simply devoted myself completely to the sea, the beach, and summer.

name: Summer Hut
description: The cool and the shade aren't the only things worth enjoying – it's also the clarity of knowing what exactly I want. This may just be a humble hut, but here I've found what I'm truly after. That's enough.

name: Beach Patrol Dog
description: He keeps a close eye on the safety of all beach-goers and sometimes helps out the losing side in a water fight.

name: Singing Emma
description: Lillian's beloved doll Emma. Not only is it her duty to play with Lillian, she is also silently guarding a secret.

name: Magical Snow Globe
description: A memento from Angelia - a snow globe with an unknown flower inside. Give it a shake and sparkly yellow pollen will swirl around. The sight of it gives the Commander nightmares, but the Dolls love it.

name: Town Musicians of Bremen Poster
description: There is a famous band in Bremen that consists of a rooster, a cat, a hound, and a donkey. Please stop commenting on the lead singer, Herr Hund's appearance. There's nothing strange about it, he's just a regular dog.

name: Shark Onesie
description: A certain Doll used to wear this in the dorm, but she couldn't bear being gawked at by the other Dolls, so she dumped it in a warehouse. That night, this onesie's popularity peaked.

name: Cozy Campfire
description: There are still cozy spots in a refugee camp where violence is prohibited. Though real life can't be saved like a game, at least you can sit by the campfire, relax, and roast a few sweet potatoes.

name: Uniform of Fantasy
description: A set of uniform that appears out of nowhere after a night's sleep. It's been meticulously laundered, but that person's scent still lingers...

name: Lunar Palace
description: It is human nature to wish for companionship in periods of loneliness, just like how people looking at this small creature wish for it to be able to understand the meaning of unity.

name: Poster - 2020 Far Side of The Sea
description: 2020 Summer Event - Special poster for Far Side of The Sea

name: Poster - Dual Randomness
description: 2022 9th Major Event - Special poster for Dual Randomness

name: Halloween Parade Float
description: The parade float glides slowly down the road with joyful music in the air. The surrounding crowd look expectantly at the float, only to find it empty. Just as they sigh in disappointment, they hear an ethereal voice singing from within the cage...

name: Evocation Stroller
description: A doll lies all alone in an unattended stroller. The white flower tied to the canopy flutters in the night breeze and exudes a peculiar fragrance. As the bell tolls, the doll blinks, and her face contorts into a grotesque grin.

name: Wind-Up Clown Dog
description: Since it's just a dog, it can't testify against the culprit who dressed him like this. All it can do is wag its tail pitifully and hope a kind person would come along and wind it up.

name: Visual Analysis Display Board
description: Whoever left these clues behind must've shared our vision - to save this shattered world and rebuild a home in which we can all put down our arms and live in peace.

name: Dark Zone Stash
description: Garbage stinks, but thanks to it, you won't become another sack of garbage that the living finds stinky. Survive, succeed...then go take a shower.

name: Encrypted Supply Crates
description: These special supply crates can be obtained by paying the corresponding amount of credits. The loot could net you a profit, but the seller will never suffer a loss. Kalina is eyeing this transaction model with great interest.

name: Temporary Resting Point
description: Where dangerous goods were once stored is now your resting point. Sleep can replenish your energy. Before you die from chemical erosion, you are the last hope in the dark.

name: "Road Closed"
description: We might find the supplies we need in here, or it could be the scene of the next catastrophe. Who cares, it'll do as long as it can shield you from bullets for now.

name: Starry Night Dreams - To the Moon
description: You don't like crowded places? Me too.

name: Starry Night Dreams - White Chest
description: Regardless if you're opening a treasure chest or Pandora's box, enjoy the story to your heart's content!

name: Starry Night Dreams - Directionless Cruise
description: It does not matter where we go. Regardless if we're sailing against the wind,  I will always travel with you.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Sheep Bodega (Left)
description: She failed to catch the crab, and so she missed the last piece of the goodwill that the story had shown her.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Sheep Bodega (Right)
description: She failed to catch the crab, and so she missed the last piece of the goodwill that the story had shown her.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Red Rabbit and Ivory
description: It only becomes a lie when it is exposed, so a lie that has not been exposed is simply the truth.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Hornless Unicorn
description: It doesn't matter if it has a horn or not when you really need it.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Hanashirube
description: The budding flower guided me to set foot on a journey...and so a promise was made.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Cruising the Galaxy
description: The ultimate question for all developed civilizations of the galaxy - Where to go for lunch?

name: Starry Night Dreams - White Queen
description: There was fruit jam yesterday and there will be fruit jam tomorrow, but there's none today. Never was, never will.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Story Collections of the Full Moon and the Sea
description: Ultimately in the end, the storyteller and those whose stories are being told reunites once again, and the moon contentedly went to sleep.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Arch of Roses and Crystals
description: Good, everyone is present now. Let the final game begin.

name: Starry Night Dreams - Lighting Up Fireflies
description: Being able to meet you in this city... Thank you...

name: Springday Classroom - Student Desk (Nap Mode)
description: The biggest disadvantage compared to resting by leaning on your desk is that you can't read manga under the cover of your coat.

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Podium
description: A short few centimeters and it gives the adults that stand on it a sense of accomplishment as if they've conquered the world.

name: Springday Classroom - Student Chair (Lesson Mode)
description: The angle of the chair skews based on the degree of chattiness you have with your friends.

name: Springday Classroom - Student Chair (Classroom Mode)
description: This mode can also be activated during a lesson to copy homework and play with your phone.

name: Springday Classroom - School Lockers
description: What hides inside is a common trope for school setting light novels and...horror games.

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Blackboard
description: Holds all sorts of precious memories. Well, most of your youth was spent looking at this thing, after all!

name: Springday Classroom - Student Desk (Classroom Mode)
description: Don't leave your videogames or magazines inside unless you can come to the classroom earlier than the teacher the next day!

name: Springday Classroom - Student Desk (Afterschool Mode)
description: A mode developed for the ease of classroom cleaning. Depending on the school, either the student on duty stacks up all the chairs or everybody does it themselves.

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Lectern
description: Final exams, answer sheets, and class marks have always touched this surface before they get handed out.  "I'm the Alpha and the Omega!"

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Floor
description: Rarely will the floor be littered with snack food wrappers and other garbage, except during sports days.

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Wallpaper
description: Leaning on the wall feels much more comfortable than leaning back in your chair, so many kind-hearted schools will regularly switch up the seating plan.

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Bulletin Board
description: The most frequent conversation that occurs just before a class: "What class do we have next?" "I forgot. Check for yourself."

name: Springday Classroom - School Shelf
description: People shouldn't be proud to be a part of a group, but rather they should make the group proud to have them as a part of it.

name: Springday Classroom - School PA System
description:
"Everyone, the broadcast starts now! I'm..." 
"Just forget it, sis. Nobody even gets it anymore..."

name: Springday Classroom - Classroom Windows
description: One day we will head out into the outside world that we yearned for, and suddenly look back... Life is full of missed opportunities, isn't it?

name: Holiday Promenade - Town Pigeons Decoration
description: They're only hologram projections as the real pigeons are always late.

name: Holiday Promenade - Town Cruise Ship Decoration
description: We sail on the lake of destiny. Heavy waves chain us to today, but they will also lead us to tomorrow.

name: Holiday Promenade - Outdoor Bench
description: When you're striking up a conversation with a lost princess, don't forget that she is sitting on the spot of the bench where you stepped on to tie your shoes.

name: Holiday Promenade - Outdoor Chair (Left)
description: I want to sit in the coffee shop by the street, go shopping, and stroll in the rain. Unfortunately, these are not adventures that I go on alone by myself.

name: Holiday Promenade - Outdoor Chair (Right)
description: I want to sit in the coffee shop by the street, go shopping, and stroll in the rain. Unfortunately, these are not adventures that I go on alone by myself.

name: Holiday Promenade - Outdoor Sunshade
description: Forget about your ideals. Sit down and pay first. Life is more than just dreams and wishes. There is still the present that you have to take care of.

name: Holiday Promenade - Street Lights
description: Bid your farewells to your heart's content, dear lovers. You have all the time in the world.

name: Holiday Promenade - Electric Moped
description: In order to prevent certain T-Dolls from acting out scenes from movies that would send the Commander flying, please limit your speed and ensure that your passenger is holding onto you.

name: Holiday Promenade - Newsstand
description: Want a newspaper? Evaluate the distance between you and the world today.

name: Holiday Promenade - Town Mailbox
description: "You've seen my world...but I've only imagined yours. Make me. Make me real!"

name: Holiday Promenade - Cobblestone Pavement
description: You hear the click clack sound of heels striking against the cobblestone pavement and you come to realize that it is fate, not time, that determines your love.

name: Holiday Promenade - Outdoor Table
description: "Are you alone?" "No, I'm waiting for someone." This is the last bit of benevolence left to him by the script.

name: Holiday Promenade - Scenic Town Background
description: "I'm looking at the people here and it must be very interesting to live here." Nevertheless, you should wake up from your holiday and return to your normal daily life.

name: Museum Trip - Gallery Bench
description: Feel free to have a seat. The dinosaur here will not pounce on you, and the tank here will not aim at you. This is the peace that you've pursued for your entire life.

name: Museum Trip - Gallery Red Carpet
description: The long carpet guides us to where we're suppose to go. But what about fate? Is it willing to be as straightforward?

name: Museum Trip - Contemporary Weaponry Display
description: Firearms and bombs have allowed humans to detach themselves from the act of killing. It has never been easier in civilized times to stir up hatred.

name: Museum Trip - Ancient Weaponry Display
description: Melee weapons required the user to come face to face with enemy. Combat required more skill, more courage, and a simpler reason to fight.

name: Museum Trip - Modern Weaponry Display
description: This era utilizes entirely new tactical weaponry, but whether war will be even more cruel or not depends entirely upon you, Commander.

name: Museum Trip - Penguin Specimen
description: These ancient and lovable birds have witnessed all the foolish things humans have done since the Third World War in their home settlements and were tragically swept up in the chaos.

name: Museum Trip - Gallery Rope Barriers
description: It separates you from history. Only history is eternal. And you? You're temporary.

name: Museum Trip - Whale Model
description: Even a real specimen is hard to find nowadays. But it's okay, mankind. You don't need to pretend like you actually care about us.

name: Museum Trip - Dinosaur Skull
description: "ROAR!"  It introduced the concept of "cool" to children around the world. It is unwittingly the earliest and purest of romances.

name: Museum Trip - Dinosaur Skeleton
description: Its elegant appearance is far more beautiful than the corpulent mammals, so Homo Sapiens gave them feathers out of spite and envy.

name: Museum Trip - Gallery Floor Tiles
description: Neat and clean floor tiles are always suitable for any sort of public spaces, but smokers and human younglings always ruin the atmosphere.

name: Museum Trip - Primates' Stump Chair
description: Any sort of entertainment is simply a substitute to satisfying bloodlust, which most likely came from the fact that food and shelter was plentiful and the brain never had a chance to develop beyond its basal instincts.

name: Museum Trip - Gallery Corridor
description: Don't mind the "History of Predation" banners. The ancestors of humanity have always relied upon extermination to build the civilized society that we have today.

name: Museum Trip - Paper Airplane
description: Perhaps on the Day of Judgment, the Creator will say this was the invention that pleased me the most.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Bench
description: This isn't a suitable bench for chance meetings. It's only good for waiting for the trains.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Train Schedule
description: A reminder of how much time you have before you need to look away from your phone. Perhaps you should've put it away a long time ago and did something proper for once.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Ticket Gate
description: A machine for testing human intelligence. Tests include how to swipe metro passes and how to bring large pieces of luggage through the gates.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Ticket Machine
description: The obstacles in your path to your faraway destination: your fellow human beings that take forever to find the change for a subway ticket.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Management Server
description: Like the humans passing by, its way to express exhaustion is to die and leave a mess.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Service Desk
description: Thousands pass by every day, but it does not mean that she isn't lonely.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Passengers Hologram Projection
description: I hear the winds from the subway and the sea of people. I'm lining up with a number plate but they were all stolen away.

name: Subway 2063 - Platform Barricade
description: How pitiful is it that people only pay attention to it when it fails to do what it was created to do.

name: Subway 2063 - Platform Floor Tiles
description: Perhaps there's a story behind every footprint. Whose path will you coincide with?

name: Subway 2063 - Platform Wall
description: The world outside has already fallen asleep, yet there are many that had just awakened from their dreams.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Train (Tail End)
description: This metal can is always stuffed full of food, but the reality is that a real monster has never appeared before.

name: Subway 2063 - Subway Train Car
description: You need a seat, a book, and a talking black cat to remind you what you're doing right now.

name: Subway 2063 - Platform Next Stop Sign
description: If you have a destination in mind then you'll know this detour isn't that big of a deal.

name: Colorful Club - School Air Mattress
description: The usage of it indoors and outdoors is not the same. Neither is its purpose in the game and in reality.

name: Colorful Club - Club Member Chair
description: The inability to spin hints at its existance as a chair for commoners, although it does come with the advantage of not slipping out under you when you're taking an afternoon nap.

name: Colorful Club - Club Member Chair
description: The inability to spin hints at its existance as a chair for commoners, although it does come with the advantage of not slipping out under you when you're taking an afternoon nap.

name: Colorful Club - School Band Instruments
description: Forget the anime. Only the vocalist with the speech disorder and the 300kg drummer can bring the hype and excitement.

name: Colorful Club - Club Room Whiteboard
description: 90% of the content on the board are nonsense, but great inspirations are born from foolish ideas.

name: Colorful Club - School Photocopier
description: Oppression of the students in the forms of tests and quizzes are spit out from this machine!

name: Colorful Club - School Bookcases
description: Few people care about what's stored here, except when they're bored out of their minds waiting for orders.

name: Colorful Club - Club Room Floor
description: A simple and durable floor. You can differentiate between the footsteps of a student and a teacher by the sound alone.

name: Colorful Club - Club Desk
description: Anything bothering you? Let's hear all about it. My pals and I are always keeping our ears open for the latest gossip.

name: Colorful Club - Club Computer Desk
description: It's just an act. Who even seriously needs to use a computer at school if not to slack off?

name: Colorful Club - Club Room Walls
description: The neat and tidy walls make you feel a sense of deference. The adults also want the children to believe as if they were gods.

name: Colorful Club - Club Room Paintings
description: Paintings of those at the top of the organization. Orders are different from religion. We never signal virtue.

name: Colorful Club - Club Room Windows
description: No matter how wonderful the outside world is, let us create precious memories now in the present.

name: City Studio - Changing Room
description: The curtains are translucent in order to prevent tactical girls from hiding inside and taking a nap. Although it is quite an invasion of privacy, it does work pretty well.

name: City Studio - Roller High Stool
description: The leather cushion has a nice sense of quality to it, and the heavy cast iron base lets the user feel at ease. Spinning on it at high speeds may send you flying.

name: City Studio - Modern Art Photo
description: If this photo is real then does Squad 404 really sing at wedding ceremonies when they're not out on missions? Then let us give the newlyweds our blessings...

name: City Studio - Photography Studio Set
description: No background is more versatile than a white one as it allows you to highlight the outline of the model. The post processing technician is also very happy with this setup as he hates floors and tiles the most.

name: City Studio - Photography Lighting A
description: "Why do the people in the pictures I take with my camera's flash end up looking like ghosts?" "Because you don't have these things. A camera's built-in flash is for amateurs."

name: City Studio - Photography Lighting B
description: "Why do the people in the pictures I take with my camera's flash end up looking like ghosts?" "Because you don't have these things. A camera's built-in flash is for amateurs."

name: City Studio - Origami Lamp
description: "A paper lamp is trendy and eco-friendly, and it gives the users a sense of involvement from folding the paper themselves. Most importantly, we can also cut costs with these!" "Clever!"

name: City Studio - Fashion Rack
description: On it hangs many classic outfits that the girls dream of wearing. Sadly, different body shapes means that loose clothes around the chest or tight clothes around the butt are inevitable.

name: City Studio - Dark Floor
description: A dark floor does not stain easily and does not interfere with the shooting by reflecting light off of the ground.

name: City Studio - Printer Set
description: Color management is a deeply profound area of study. Even if your screen color is very accurate, the printers at the print shop may not be. It's best to send a physical copy over as well, just in case.

name: City Studio - Post Processing Workstation
description: Shooting with a medium format camera and a high performance all-in-one camera together allows you examine the results in real-time. Greatly increased efficiency, but also a completely emptied wallet.

name: City Studio - Industrial Walls
description: Even though the stars in the screens are fake, the smiles of the girls under the spotlight are real. They might've been able to become shining stars of the highest caliber if we were in peacetime.

name: City Studio - Paintings Collection
description: To deliberately hang these paintings neatly yet disorganized is an art in and of itself. Just a little bit of carelessness may inflict sleepless nights onto the commanders that suffer from OCD.

name: Moonlight Ball - Python Patterned Bench
description: When the design itself can no longer define luxury, people turn their attention to the materials used, so many wild animals were made into furniture in the 19th and 20th centuries.

name: Moonlight Ball - Persian Rug
description: This magnificent handmade Persian rug is a real antique borrowed from Mr. Kruger's private collection to keep up appearances, so try not to step on it. Hey, hey, P7!

name: Moonlight Ball - Bust Sculpture
description: You know this is a downright despotic enterprise when you see a sculpture of the head of the company in the corridor.

name: Moonlight Ball - Pipe Organ
description: From Bach to Mendelssohn, the organ has always been the most dominant weapon in the composer's hands. Now, it is equipped with an electric blower, making it much easier to use.

name: Moonlight Ball - Zeppelin Airship
description: Even if it has long been rendered obsolete, an airship will forever fantasize about casting its huge, elegant shadow on the face of the earth. An airplane can never compare in this regard.

name: Moonlight Ball - Classical Round Table
description: Spread on the gorgeous table is an old sheepskin scroll that has documented the extravagant recipes of the artistocrats from the past. Perhaps we should have Springfield take a look at it.

name: Moonlight Ball - Marble Tiles
description: Heels of the crystal slippers fill the ball with the sound of crisp clinks. The marble floor reflects the girls' gorgeous figures. At least for tonight, let the music continue.

name: Moonlight Ball - Crystal Chandelier
description: A crystal chandelier was once the product of craftsmen's years of experience and hardwork and was a symbol of wealth and status due to its high cost and difficulty in cleaning. Now they can simply be 3D printed.

name: Moonlight Ball - Spiral Staircase
description: A huge spiral staircase is essential for a grand entrance to a ball and as a temporary seating for tactical girls that are not accustomed to wearing high heels. Very practical.

name: Moonlight Ball - Palace Walls
description: Walls, hallways, and floor-to-ceiling windows that always appear in fairy tale castles. People like splendorous architecture so much that they started a neoclassical movement.

name: Moonlight Ball - Sword and Shield Decoration
description: "Will our guns also be hung up on a wall as a decoration someday?" "They will. Perhaps when the world achieves world peace~ or when they come up with an even more convenient way of killing people."

name: Children's Playground - Multicolored Starry Floor
description: "That's right, this is the sky. There is a small village of elves living on the ceiling. They're waiting for me."

name: Children's Playground - Jigsaw Puzzle Carpet
description: "Who won last time? ...Wait, did I play Aeroplane Chess or Monopoly last time?"

name: Children's Playground - Kids Bookshelf
description: "Before you grow up, this is your journey. After you grow up, this will be your treasure."

name: Children's Playground - Miniature Railway Engine
description: "Toot toot! Where do you want to go? We're only going to places not on the map!"

name: Children's Playground - Miniature Railway Carriage
description: "Is the next one your station? Are you gonna leave us? You'll come back to see us, right?"

name: Children's Playground - Round Table with Building Blocks
description: "Welcome. Here are castles, skyscrapers, monsters of all sorts, as well as your childhood."

name: Children's Playground - Plush Bear Chair
description: "It's filled with candies... Shh, I'll tell only you where the secret pocket is."

name: Children's Playground - Inflatable Horse Seat
description: "Are we really gonna defeat those enemies, Miss Knight? Why don't we go and chat with them first?"

name: Children's Playground - Car Sofa
description: "Sorry, we're full. I'm afraid that someone will have to get off the car... Hey! Don't kick!"

name: Children's Playground - Pirate Ship Double Bed
description: "What are we going to do with these little drunk sailors? ...Of course we're gonna tuck them in under the blankets for a good night's sleep!"

name: Children's Playground - Applique Wallpaper
description: "Promise us that even if this place is one day filled with awards and certificates, don't forget us, and don't forget yourself."

name: Children's Playground - Butterfly Ceiling Lamps
description: "Fly! Fly while your dreams are still light and airy, fly towards the castle of the future!"

name: Children's Playground - Starry Sky Window
description: "No matter how big the universe is, you and us will forever be a part of it."

name: Candy Town - Sunshine Bubblegum Floor
description: Too many people walking on it will cause it to become bubbles and rise into the sky, so there are usually multiple layers of bubblegum flooring. It also helps to keep track of the number of daily visitors.

name: Candy Town - Long Cream Biscuit Road
description: The long and thin Pokey sticks each have individual and deep thoughts. They will cause any trespassing car to slide off completely.

name: Candy Town - Crunchy Ice Cream Road Sign
description: Carving on it is a task full of ordeals. Many people will either break the crunchy outer layer accidentally or eat it carefully.

name: Candy Town - Candy Jar Country Soldier
description: The Candy Jar Country and Snack Barrel Country often go to war over cream. The loser will have no choice but to use their milk powder as paint for that month.

name: Candy Town - Snack Barrel Country Soldier
description: Wars between the two countries often stall because the soldiers ate their own weapons. In the end, they decide victory through honey-drinking competitions.

name: Candy Town - Frosty Ice Cream Streetlights
description: Because it melts so easily, it can only be used at night... Oh? Don't human streetlights function on the same principle?

name: Candy Town - Dreamy Smoothie Shop
description: Will sweets be sold in a city built from candies? Or will a world where humans and animals coexist peacefully have zoos?

name: Candy Town - Mocha Cocoa Racecar
description: It was tough getting my hands on a genuine racecar like this! After all, mocha art had disappeared from the human world long ago!

name: Candy Town - Chocolate Profiterole Bench
description: Although it's comfortable, don't sleep on it for too long. It will melt if you dream of warm things.

name: Candy Town - Catty Cake Bus
