 "Some signposts aren't there to point the way. They're there to remind you of the importance of 'directions'."

name: Debut Poster
description: No matter how much time has passed, they will always remember that moment - when they stood on the stage with their dreams, uncertainty, and passion. All the effort was worth it.

name: Master of Wealth
description:
Take the money out of your pockets and be the master of wealth. If you can't do that, you will be its slave instead and toil your life away.
 "...Why are you all staring at me?" - Kalina

name: Master of Fate
description:
Trust your destiny and be the master of fate. Even if you can't roll a 6, at least roll something less pathetic than a 1.
 "Glory be to Griffin."

name: Outer Polaris
description: A promotional poster for a movie when it was first shown in the theaters. Some people say it's a movie that portrays the reality of being an astronomer, while others say it's a romance disguised as soft sci-fi.

name: Perfect Tea Party
description: The best barista + the best pâtissierre = the perfect tea party.

name: Fresh Turf
description: The grass here was only grown this year – it has never seen blood or fire. Individual blades crowd together around a sword and wonder, “Is this blade also one of us?”

name: Distant Sky
description: The sky does change, but people always have more important things to do than watching the sky. There's their studies, family, fortune, or even just an adventure to seek freedom.

name: Food Cart
description: Before seeing the owner, nobody can say for certain if this food cart has visited other cities before. How about an apple, my dear?

name: Ancient City Wall
description: Many things in the world are a cycle, like war and peace, death and birth… The city wall doesn't fear its own destruction – it knows that one day, it will inevitably crumble to ash and dust again to nurture new flowers.

name: Flourishing Shrub
description: The wind tells the shrub that thousands of years ago, its ancestors were so tall they could touch the sky. The shrub asks, “So they wouldn't be chewed on by rabbits?” The wind replies, “That's right. The only thing that would munch them were dinosaurs.”

name: Mobile Signpost
description: A child once turned the signpost out of curiosity to direct inexperienced adventurers straight to the demon overlord's lair. Ever since then, the signpost has been moved to somewhere high up on a mountain. For some reason, it was never moved back to where it's supposed to be.

name: Noticeboard
description: A noticeboard permanently set up outside the city. Apart from the usual wanted posters, there are also notices such as, “Do not take off your clothes and walk to the public bath naked.”

name: Tattered Banner
description: This banner was torn by children. The grown-ups who moved away have left it behind as a prayer for new children to be born here when the war was over.

name: Wind-Worn Wall
description: The bricks and tiles from the same era as this crumbled wall have already been reduced to ash and dust. It can no longer hold back enemies like it used to, but if children seek refuge behind it, it might still be able to block a few lethal bullets – which may be why it still hasn't collapsed.

name: Storage Crate
description: Sorry, but the old stool got smashed. If you're tired, just sit on this for a while. Don't mind the two swords – their owners aren't coming back for them.

name: Traveler's Luggage
description: You're rested and ready to start your journey? Then take these with you. I ask nothing of you except that you come back alive and tell me all about your adventures.

name: Party Wine Table
description: The last person to sit at this table said, “When I return, I shall replace this old thing with a grandiose long table – the kind used by the aristocrats!” And? It's still the same table now. What did you expect?

name: Temporary Stall
description: Are you sure about this? You're heading straight into hell! Are you really not turning back? At least buy a gun and take it with you. It will come in useful. Even if you don't survive, at least the money you pay me will keep me alive a little longer.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Textured Flooring
description: The texture is synthetic, but the sweat and tears on the floor aren't.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Silent Night Sky
description: Artificial light may outshine the moon and the stars, but they are still watching over you, bearing witness as you trudge forward along this path time and time again.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Izakaya Bar Table
description: The prices of all goods here, except for the barkeeper's companionship, are marked clearly.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Izakaya Signboard
description: The shop and the customers are all old friends, but the signboard is regularly replaced – can't be helped, the prices have to go up along with inflation.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Izakaya Wallpaper
description: "This wallpaper looks pretty new." "The frequency of its replacement depends on how many people throw drunken fits in here in a month."

name: Griffin Izakaya – Glimpse of an Alley
description: Take this alley to go home if you're drunk. It's pretty quiet in here, and no one cares about your disheveled state.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Sliding Door (Left)
description: It believes that it has been given too much advertising work that doesn't fall within its scope of duty. "This won't do," it thinks worriedly. "At this rate, I'll be no different than a human."

name: Griffin Izakaya – Sliding Door (Right)
description: Even though it's made of paper, it can kiss the moon. It can also keep the passersby outside and hide you as you cry your heart out.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Kitchen Stove
description: The father says to his child, "This is the flame of our worldly existence." The mother then asks the father, "Can you do the dishes already?"

name: Griffin Izakaya – Breezy Round Stool
description: This is a lovely spot to have a drink and enjoy the breeze. You can relish your freedom and feast your eyes on the bustling scenery, even if all you have is a cup of water.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Roadside Vending Machine
description: No need for ingratiating flattery or contrived schemes. As long as you have money, you can have the things sold here. So cough up the cash.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Table of Late Conversation
description: Ordering a one-person set meal makes you feel lonely? Don't think of it that way. You have the condiment on the table and the moon as your company.

name: Griffin Izakaya – Faux Floorboard
description: Genuine timber is very valuable in this day and age – as if I could afford to lay the floor of an izakaya with such expensive materials! This isn't a White Zone, you know?

name: Old Town Stroll – Gravel Flooring
description: I know hardships await you on your journey, but old friends are akin to family. Don't forget to return when your business is concluded and walk down this road once more.

name: Old Town Stroll – Mansion in the Sunset
description: Look! Even the sun and the clouds are enchanted by the cherry blossoms – they're swooning and tumbling down!

name: Old Town Stroll – Hawker's Cart
description: This is a place of nostalgic flavors. The person who once brought you here now needs to lean on you as they walk.

name: Old Town Stroll – Soba Restaurant
description: Don't mix your sighs into the noodles. You'll only end up with a bowl of bitter soup.

name: Old Town Stroll – Dried Well
description: If we compare a bucket falling into water to a person's death, then a well is a metaphor for the mortal world. How many thousands of times has this bucket been reincarnated?

name: Old Town Stroll – Snow-Melting Bathhouse
description: Let me weave a shawl for you with steam to melt away the snow that envies you.

name: Old Town Stroll - Noh Masks Stall
description: As you gently stroke the pattern on the mask, you'll be drawn in by the story it tells.

name: Old Town Stroll – Retro Inn
description: The flowers have bloomed. The innkeeper opens the door, letting the fragrance swirl around the lodgers' ankles.

name: Old Town Stroll – Regal Sakura
description: Blossoms which have fallen off can never return to their original branch, but travelers can always go home.

name: Old Town Stroll – Clean Water Stall
description: Dreams above the clouds, water in a dream; a cart in the streets, a traveler before you.

name: Old Town Stroll – Terrace of Silence
description: When one is heartbroken, raindrops should splatter on the roof to drown out the sound of tears.

name: Old Town Stroll – Pagoda of Zen
description: People say that the only constant in life is change, yet people also aspire to create constant, enduring things.

name: Old Town Stroll – Cart with Goods
description: As the spring breeze whirls past the wheels, it can already smell the autumn of abundant harvest from the flowers.

name: Old Town Stroll – Courtyard Bench
description: The night is free of both rain and people. A bird lands on the bench and pecks at the scattered petals.

name: Bunker - Grid Reference Flooring
description: This flooring with neat grids will aid you in managing the interior space and finding anomalies. It will also trigger people with OCD.

name: Bunker - Silent Witness
description: Until its destruction, it will be here to support the ceiling and bear whatever decoration humans want to put on it. But don't feel sorry for it - it will probably still be standing long after you're gone.

name: Bunker - Data Processing Station
description: Since phones are banned, these two computers are the only equipment with access to the outside world. Whoever built this bunker didn't consider the possibility that the network connection could be severed.

name: Bunker - Loafer Office Chair
description: A comfy chair gets worn-out very soon - just like a competent agent.

name: Bunker - Dirt-Removing Rugs
description: These rugs are great at removing dirt and blood caked in your soles. Stains may be a source of annoyance to others, but to them, they are medals to be worn with pride.

name: Bunker - Informational Blackboard
description: A relatively new blackboard. Every once in a while, an agent would write out their vision for the future to help them through the long and lonely nights.

name: Bunker - "Cozy Moments"
description: The warm-toned lights help people relax. In these long, cold, and lonely nights, even the illusion of warmth is greatly treasured.

name: Bunker - Projection Whiteboard
description: It's hard to upgrade the equipment in here, so our clever logistics officer created a new briefing tool by combining a whiteboard and a projector. "Just pretend it's a touch screen."

name: Bunker - Miscellaneous Toolkits
description: The creator of this bunker has spent a lot of effort to ensure that agents have access to useful tools in emergencies.

name: Bunker - Emergency Supplies
description: Even if the chances are one in a billion, we must prepare for the possibility - that's what sets us apart.

name: Bunker - Weapon Supply Crates
description: It's fine if the equipment doesn't get upgraded, but our gear must be the coolest. Still, reasons like "I want to dual-wield shotguns on the battlefield" won't cut it - don't make life difficult for our logistics officer!

name: Bunker - "Before You Go"
description: We may never come back here again, so think about what to take and what to leave behind before you go.

name: Bunker - Live Plant
description: Please water it and care for it properly. If the air circulation system breaks down, it'll be your only hope.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Boundless Snowfield
description: Pixel by pixel, just like snow... As long as they all fit perfectly together, it will extend forever and ever, to infinity.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Aurora Borealis
description: Beautiful sights either bring people joy or remind them of their loneliness.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Ski Equipment Store
description: In order to ensure all customers can enjoy their time, they can purchase ski equipment here even if they forget to bring their own! For the sake of sacred profit, anything is possible!

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Miraculous Fast Food Stall
description: Compared to being lucky enough to remain oblivious to the rigged prices, it's much better to enjoy "miracles" that one can simply purchase with money!

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Witch's Palace
description: The magical ball will come to an end when the clock strikes twelve. The alarm has been deactivated, so keep eating! Nothing can stop us from indulging ourselves!

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Protective Fence
description: If the snow grows thin, it's probably not getting warmer; some kids might have climbed over the fence.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Ski Lift
description: This ski lift used to be called "Challenger". Now there are no more challengers, and the lift is all that remains.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Dasher's Steed
description: Ride it and temporarily skid off the ground. Leave your family and your anxiety behind; let the sense of thrill wipe your mind completely blank. Even if your troubles are never far behind, at least right now, you are no one but a dasher in the snow.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Winter Supplies
description: Don't touch them - they're just props made from painted concrete. Humans are creatures that desperately need a sense of security; they are always trying to confirm their ties with nature through some kind of archaic activity.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Visitor Notice
description: This is a VERY detailed list of dos and don'ts - brimming with the businesses' fear and aversion to taking responsibility.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Wooden Chair of Relaxation (Left)
description: One must have a place to rest after an adventure. Please spread this - save the chair!

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Wooden Chair of Relaxation (Right)
description: One must have a place to rest after an adventure. For every adventurer who doesn't rest, there is an unemployed chair.

name: Dashing Through the Snow - Dreamy Dining Table
description: According to Dreamy, it requires certain effort from humans to ensure the meal is actually warm when the diners arrive. "Even dreams are time-based."

name: Snowflake in Tea - Frosty Gravel
description: Before the snow arrives, the cold has already kissed the ground.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Cold Mountain Snow
description: Everything falls silent in the snow, but the snow is full of noise.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Ancient Irori
description: Fire rejects winter's gift and lets people freely enjoy its warmth and hazard.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Chest of Drawers
description: If all the world's treasures amount to 8 units, I own 10 units, while everyone else owes me 2 units. - Stechkin

name: Snowflake in Tea - Witness of Time
description: Each wound is a concession to the snow; each new bud is the start of a new resistance.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Waiting for Sprouts
description: The withered tree had a dream. It dreamed that young fledglings once again populate the nest in the safety of its dense foliage.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Wind-Proof Sliding Doors
description: The innocence of youth and the maturity that comes with age are mutually exclusive. Now make your choice - will you throw out the unruly children to suffer in the cold, or will you let them stay at the risk of them wrecking your doors?

name: Snowflake in Tea - Stately Walls
description: A respectable mansion needs stately enclosing walls and an equally stately entrance. Dignity starts from the porch and ends with your depleted wallet.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Dream-Lit Flame
description: The original idea behind this design was to let people meditate in style on a cold winter night, but the architect seemed to have forgotten that the cold can paralyze human thought.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Brand New Tatami
description: To obtain the optimal airiness and temperature, we've secretly installed underfloor heating. Now we just have to worry about potential fire hazards.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Enenra of Dusk
description: A moon purchased with money will never wane; artificial flowers will never wilt, but beauty that never changes loses its meaning. Humans are such a fussy species.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Bridge of Frozen Rain
description: With the bridge bearing all the weight, water can go and seek out snow without a care, ultimately turning into beautiful fractals.

name: Snowflake in Tea - Spring of Youth
description: If you want to enjoy the hot springs in winter, you must first endure the cold - it's fate. So why didn't the architect design a wind-proof hallway that leads directly to the springs? Fire him!

name: New Year Market - Rhombus Grid Carpet
description: The carpet is changed once a year. Out with the old and in with the new. It has been baptized by children's excrement, teenagers' chewing gum, and adults' cigarette butts. You could say the carpet has experienced a lifetime in a matter of days.

name: New Year Market - Fireworks of Mortality
description: People who value traditions are very good at cranking up the festive atmosphere using fireworks and crackers. The racket can also force those who go to bed early to stay up for Lunar New Year.

name: New Year Market - "2022"
description: Starting from today, people need a new diary to record the time that they will proceed to waste.

name: New Year Market - "Spring"
description: Good fortune comes with spring to breathe new life into all of creation. Will the new year bring fewer calamities? Everyone wants that to be true.

name: New Year Market - Promotional Platform
description: Hey, look over here, friends! This is the 2022 Lunar New Year Auspicious Big Bundle available only at our store... What? We sold the same stuff last year? Nonsense. These are more expensive!

name: New Year Market - Auspicious Rug
description: This rug is very lucky. It is perfectly content as long as it gets stepped on by pretty girls in stilettos. It also likes making them trip every now and then.

name: New Year Market - Promotional Monitor
description: Red light draws attention from a greater distance. It hopes that these blessings are conveyed to everyone who sees it.

name: New Year Market - Event Light Rig
description: Neon lights are harsh on the eyes but also the most eye-catching. People are always drawn to things that are harmful to them.

name: New Year Market - Camera Combo
description: Most of the stuff recorded on camera won't be played a second time, but people never get tired of this. As long as something makes you happy, it's worth it.

name: New Year Market - Stage Backdrop
description: A backdrop that's redecorated every year, featuring all elements that evoke "auspicious festivities". The set designer said he did his best.

name: New Year Market - New Year Lantern Display
description: After multiple fire accidents, the lanterns switched out their candles for electric lights. Why can't we celebrate Lunar New Year in fiery red...?

name: New Year Market - Event Host Counter
description: A counter piled with prizes looks especially tantalizing, and the Goliath is the host's source of comfort. Even though an unused weapon is practically a toy, it's still a reassuring presence.

name: New Year Market - Celebration Lantern Display
description: After multiple fire accidents, the lanterns switched out their candles for electric lights. Hurray! More unruly kids are gonna get their hands scorched!

name: Dark Vows - Dull Grass
description: The shriveled skin of the earth is waiting to be irrigated by the tears from the sky. Are flowers its loving murmurs or a sad farewell?

name: Dark Vows - "Ardent Love"
description: Seeking love in the midst of despair is like running blindly towards the light in a dark forest. Whether you'll find it is beside the point - it's just a fictitious reason that people cling to for the sake of living.

name: Dark Vows - Banquet Table of Luxuriant Flowers
description: My love, please allow me to drape the table in silk brocade and light up the night with flowers, wine, and a vow.

name: Dark Vows - Gnarled Metal Gate
description: "Though we were off to a bad start, as long as we stay hopeful, everything will get better!" ...How many couples do you think have had this thought? And how many couples actually got what they wished for?

name: Dark Vows - Never-Ending Dreams
description: The bed is already overgrown with flowers and weeds, and I am rapidly decomposing... Why haven't you come to visit me in my dreams?

name: Dark Vows - Wooden Serving Cart
description: Light the candles! There's no need to serve any food. We'll weave spider thread into gloves, raise a bottle of wine, and drink to Time.

name: Dark Vows - Guiding Lamp
description: The iron has withstood scorching heat and terrible storms, yet it still gave in to Time. Don't admit defeat - we must be more constant than iron.

name: Dark Vows - Church of Ravens
description: Say your vows to the illusory light. O Lord, please bear witness - even if our lives are as transient as candlelight, our love is no less real.

name: Dark Vows - Board of Vows
description: Write down what you want to say. Even if your words will be washed away by the rain, at least you made an effort to immortalize them.

name: Dark Vows - Stone Path
description: If one must experience pain in the pursuit of happiness, then...is tripping on the way also a kind of bliss for a seeker of happiness?

name: Dark Vows - A Chair
description: Sit here and wait. Even if what you're waiting for doesn't show up, at least you can make your choice with dignity.

name: Dark Vows - 100 Years of Solitude
description: Our story may not be anything new, but those in the story are no longer here. I don't want any regrets before I go...

name: Dark Vows - Altar of Vows
description: If today is the end of the world, I can solemnly declare, "I still love you, till the very end."

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Grids
description: High or low, far or near, treacherous or even... One wrong move could affect the outcome atop these grids.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Silent Woods
description: This is the perfect spot for an ambush, but you must also consider the possibility that your opponent has anticipated your move.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Gentle Spotlights
description: These lights bear witness to each match. They illuminate an endless battle of wits.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – In the Game
description: "Heh, he shouldn't have made that move. I wouldn't have made that mistake if it were me!" "I've been waiting for you to say that – it's our turn to play."

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Chessmaster
description: This chess board is a caricature of everything about war.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Slogan Sign
description: "Luffberry Chess – a chance for you to demonstrate your talent in military command!"

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Timescape
description: This is a war without gun smoke, but we can give you the illusion of being on a battlefield.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Honor
description: Victories are displayed here. Their existence signifies mankind's endless potential.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Chess Stand
description: All chess pieces are perfect facsimiles of T-Dolls so that you will have the most realistic experience in the game.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Check-Out Point
description: Once you've settled your scores with your opponents, remember to sort out the memories you are taking with you before you go.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Charred Earth
description: Rest here for a while. The fight is never over. Take some time to think things through – it can help us go even further.

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Souvenir Display
description: Haven't had enough? Why not put them on your bedside table to remind you of the good times that you spent strategizing?

name: Luffberry Chess Room – Luffberry Time
description: Welcome to the Luffberry Chess Room, Commander. It's time for a delightful match!

name: Drink the Night Away – Black Velvet Carpet
description: This kind of black velvet carpet is said to be an imitation of the feathers of a black swan – fluffy and soft. We live in comfort because we are surrounded by such things that would break our fall. Thunder, get off the floor. That's not your kind.

name: Drink the Night Away – Sunset on the City
description: The city is always bustling no matter when. The lights will drown out all sentiment and filter out the darkness, leaving only the bright and brilliant. Still, Gr MG36, it's super dangerous to climb out of the window for pictures!

name: Drink the Night Away – Digital Welcome Sign
description: The welcome sign reflects on the standard of your guests to a certain extent, which is why we try our best to make the design as exquisite as possible. That doesn't mean, General Liu, that you should be flaunting your Black Card. Put that away, please.

name: Drink the Night Away – Mixology Bar
description: Blending different liquors can create surprising flavors and sensations. I totally get you, SOP-II, but you absolutely must not approach the the bar – Commander's order!

name: Drink the Night Away – Appetizer Table
description: Juice, dessert, roses. Objects whose purpose is to create an atmosphere are mostly like this – beautiful but not satiating for the belly. But even so, we must keep WA2000 away from the kitchen. The main course is almost ready!

name: Drink the Night Away – Decorative Red Carpet
description: Creating a sense of ceremony with all kinds of decorations is a universal way of finding charm in life. You will feel dignified and glamorous like a movie star just by walking on the red carpet... Strange, did I bump into someone? I thought I heard Spectre M4.

name: Drink the Night Away – Cozy Arbor
description: Here one can enjoy the view outside while also experience the coziness of an indoor setting, which makes it the most romantic spot. Saiga places a glass of untouched beverage opposite herself to pretend that she isn't here alone.

name: Drink the Night Away – Live Plant
description: Watch out, that's our most expensive piece of furniture here! It's an actual, real plant... And it's not an herb that can be used for seasoning! Guys, keep those Chinese Dolls away!

name: Drink the Night Away – Galvanized Iron Railings
description: This floor-to-ceiling glass window has been reinforced, but we've still added railings. Not to protect the glass, but to protect the Dolls' heads. See, Gr SL8 just slammed right into it.

name: Drink the Night Away – Champagne Table
description: Ever since a drunk 416 ran around using the table as a shield and urging everyone else to find cover, we've adopted a new kind of champagne table.

name: Drink the Night Away – Bar Stools
description: These bar stools have rungs for people to rest their feet, but some of the smaller Dolls still struggle to climb on. Miss Springfield, could you prepare some milk? A consolation drink is the least these Dolls deserve.

name: Drink the Night Away – Black Gold Signboard
description: Welcome to Griffin's 5th Anniversary Celebration! What? AK-12 and AN-94? No, they're not here, which is why we've hung them on the sign!

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Illuminated Lilies
description: The marble lilies blooming voraciously under the light reflect the splendor of rebirth.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Memories and Tomorrow
description: The fragrance of wood and the elegant pattern recount memories of the past, while you, illuminated by the lights, are about to embrace a better tomorrow.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Tri-Colored Future
description: Will tomorrow be a leisurely blue, a passionate red, or a white of infinite possibility? The one who decides will always be you.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Etches of Glory
description: During night-time when everything is quiet, the tall, lean and chatty shop owner always rearranges and polishes the medals and certificates on the wall, as if to relive moments of past glory.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Drops of Memories
description: Every artist has embarked on a miraculous journey. These wall decorations are all memories of this journey.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Color Delivery
description: Even the same hairstyle will generate a different mood depending on the color—aren't colors simply incredible?

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Farewell to Yesterday
description: When you sit down on this chair, whether with anticipation or agitation, you will inevitably meet a new self. So now, please bid your yesterday farewell.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Invitation from a Reflection
description: Dear sir, allow me to introduce a new friend—this is you, who has been reborn today. I hope you get along.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Rainbow Baptism
description: The rainbow in the bottles glide over your hair; the warm rain reveals its true, vibrant hues. As your gentle baptism goes on, do tell me what you expect from your new self.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Passage of Time
description: No matter how hard it rains and storms outside, the passage of time will always be quiet and warm in here.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Awaiting Metamorphosis
description: Seated on the soft and bouncy sofa, I close my eyes and listen as the scissors snip their way through a fellow customer's hair. Time goes by quietly in this little shop as I await my brand new self.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Price of Rebirth
description: All must abide by the law of equivalent exchange. If you want to become a new you, you'll have to pay the corresponding price—but if you get the membership card...

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Verdant Tenderness
description: The shop owner always has a subtle tender look in his eyes when he is tending to his plants.

name: Rebirth in the Mirror – Warm-Toned Breeze
description: Warm, pale-yellow light fills the space in the little shop; soft, gentle breeze slips through the light and kisses the slowly flowing time.

name: Beyond Curry
description: The key to cooking a perfect pot of curry isn't picking the right spices, it's keeping your mind focused and free of stray thoughts. When you gaze long into the curry, the curry gazes also into you.

name: Basic Magic Carpet
description: There are all kinds of magic carpets in the world – some can fly and can keep you warm, some can send you into a sweet dream immediately, and some...that want nothing but to trip you.

name: Portrait of an Evil Deity
description: A portrait of unknown origin. If you pray piously in front of it… Nothing will happen. But if you offer it some good food and wine, it will all disappear in the blink of an eye.

name: Secret Conference Table
description: A conference table that is only used in the most critical moments. Multiple serious conundrums such as "what to eat for dinner" have been resolved at this table.

name: Tangan-chan
description: A creature with pretty decent eyesight and has no need for glasses, but it still occasionally laments the fact that it can't seem to find glasses that would suit it. Possibly a source of woe shared be all one-eyed demons.

name: Little Bean
description: It once thought the humans' planet was made up of soybeans because they were in all the places it had visited in the mortal world. It only found out the truth after it named itself "Little Bean".

name: Bête
description: A Beast of Gévaudan that hasn't yet reached maturity. His hobby includes napping and making friends (but only limited to other Beasts of Gévaudan of the opposite gender). He has the nasty habit of chewing on hands, so all humans except for Yurine are advised to keep their hands away from his mouth.

name: Time and the Stars
description: The hopes and dreams that a certain "Prefect" has gleaned from the stars are etched on the exquisite antique telescope.

name: Secret Record
description: A record in Suomi's prized collection. Legend has it, if you play it to someone who means a lot to you, they will understand your feelings. However, the seal on it has never been broken for some reason.

name: Gift Trap
description: Presents given out by Px4 Storm. "The point of exchanging presents is the sense of anticipation you feel before you unwrap them, right? What happens after the gifts are unwrapped doesn't concern me," —thus spoke Px4 Storm.

name: Christmas Reindeer
description: In the past, reindeer would assist Santa Claus in delivering presents and free him if he got stuck in chimneys. But as societies develop in recent years, buildings are getting taller and taller while there are fewer and fewer chimneys. Over time, people have stopped catching sight of Santa and his reindeer. Have they lost their jobs? No, they're simply protecting Christmas in some other way.

name: Chinese Pastoral Cat (Yellow)
description: A sly little one. It plays deaf when I call its name. Keeps nudging me when I'm busy or want to be alone. But whenever I'm sad or hurt, it comes curling up next to me first thing. How can I bring myself to hate it?

name: Chinese Pastoral Cat (Black)
description: Introverted, sensitive and paranoid. Ever since it was bullied into surrendering its own feeding bowl to another cat, it's been taking elastic hairbands from my room and throwing them in the trash like a vengeful spirit. Guess I'll be running out of hairbands if I don't sort this fight out soon...

name: American Shorthair
description: It may look healthy and docile, and perches quietly while I'm home, but the moment I'm out, it starts wreaking havoc like crazy. It opens all the cupboard doors, pushes my gaming console over, and destroys my pillows... It's way too healthy. Is that a good thing? Well...

name: Siamese Cat
description: A clever and clingy aristocrat. So good it could pretty much be a dog if you put a leash on it. Only meows when it's with someone close. Extremely jealous. Whenever you're hanging out with others, all it cares about is that it isn't the one you're with.

name: Serval
description: Lean and graceful. A hunter with amazing reflexes. The mothers always prepared to carry their cubs and switch dens quickly on the hostile savannahs. Domesticated servals are also very clingy... After all, who else can they rely on after leaving their natural habitats?

name: Shiba Inu
description: "Look at this adorable shiba!" "What's a shiba? You or this dog?" "I AM 'this dog', and I'm single."

name: Pug
description: "Look, this is how I promote shibas," says the last chairman, vice-chairman, counsellor, accountant and officer of the Shiba Promotional Committee, with a long sip of coke.

name: Doberman
description: The Dobermann is named after the first breeder. They're brave, strong and intelligent. However, despite their fame of being natural hunters, the breed only emerged about 100 years ago... They have less "wolf" in them than even shibas and pugs.

name: Husky
description: Ancient Siberians started domesticating local wolves to aid in their hunts, and that's how huskies came to be. They once played a crucial role in the long history of this frozen terrain, but have since gained popularity as a cute and dorky pet, making them one of the few animals that benefited from modern civilization.

name: Old English Sheepdog
description: The Old English Sheepdog isn't a particularly old breed and appeared no more than 30 years earlier than the Dobermann. Due to social and profitable reasons, old English sheepdogs had to be docked in the past, but this is becoming more and more uncommon nowadays, also due to social and profitable reasons.

name: Basset Hound
description: Although Basset Hounds are 71st in the canine IQ rankings, one can't call them stupid. "With no rabbits to chase, all it can do is keep watching movies, and now it looks a lot like that blind old gentleman who waltzes with ladies", a passing logistics officer said.

name: Pigeon
description: The pigeon represents many things in the world of human symbolism. Peace, or magic shows, for example. In reality, magicians actually just use regular pigeons for their magic acts. Perhaps this may be the pigeon's own magic trick, and the magicians are in fact the prop? Perhaps like peace, everything may just be an illusion?

name: Golden Parrotbill
description: The golden parrotbill is a bright and lively small bird that sings in the jungle and is hard to capture. But don't be discouraged, because you'll only get their response with enough patience. Believe in nature, because after all, nature believes in you.

name: Long-Eared Owl
description: Due to the destruction of habitats, this typical owl is now very rare, and its appearance is often met with the fright of human cameras. Perhaps by next winter, pictures will be the only things left of them, and people will wistfully tell themselves, "thank goodness we still have the pictures; at least they will not be forgotten..."

name: Macaw
description: Macaws were originally introduced worldwide by colonists that brought them from their hometowns. However, due to excessive hunting and habitat destruction, there may come a day when pirate stories become the only place they'll appear in, and like sea monsters, they'll just be some strange, colorful creatures that can speak.

name: Bald Eagle
description: The bald eagle possesses a divine and majestic appearance that appeals to human aesthetics. This is the reason why they've been safe from premature extinction in contrast to some other less fortunate birds. Yet, because its call sounds too cute, the movies actually dub it over with the voice of another bird; this is the essence of divinity.

name: Spotted Hamster
description: After the twelfth week of the Commander lying flat on the ground to observe this spotted hamster every day, Miss Logistics Officer immediately curbed the hamster's freedom. However, this might have been a good thing for the hamster; it seems much more at ease running around in its cage than being glared at by cats.

name: Snapping Turtle
description: There's no telling if the base's snapping turtle is too friendly or too vicious; there have already been several Doll fingers found in its stomach, probably bitten off when the Dolls tried to touch it while feeding. If you love it, perhaps it might be better to keep your distance.

name: Ferret
description: If you're out of the house often, a ferret might not be the best pet for you. Training a young ferret requires a lot of time and patience. Fortunately, Griffin is full of such people, and they've even formed a Part-Time Ferret-Rearing Squad — even if "part-time" in this case is basically equivalent to "full-time".

name: Chameleon
description: If you're very confident in your reflexes and concentration, raising a chameleon might be a good choice. After all, they're visible for only a moment when they flee, after which they vanish into your house and their corpses can't even be found.

name: Innocent Seal
description: It's just an ordinary seal. It doesn't jump around in front of humans, and it doesn't follow its observers with a penguin in its mouth. All it does is quietly waiting in the base's imitated Antarctic sector in the hope that it won't be bullied.

name: Bookshelf of Memories
description: A bookshelf stuffed full of memories.

name: Barren Valley
description: The Fairies keep insisting that they are real mythical creatures, the guardians of the forests and glens. The Commander, who'd had enough of the AIs' endless badgering, finally decided to build them a suitable living environment.

name: Mountain Fort
description: After some hard work, the Commander built a medieval castle in the middle of styrofoam mountains. With this, other facilities can also be leveled up now. (Mind the ventilation when spraying paint!)

name: Fairy Hall
description: The Fairies think that they deserve a more grandiose home that better reflects their rapidly rising status. This neoclassical white hall seems fitting.

name: Fairy Palace
description: The final form complete with white towers and an outer wall. The pleased Fairies are already chattering nonstop and demanding the addition of a peerage system. It seems like there is still a market for feudal monarchy.

name: Dusty Railway Model
description: The shape of a railway model peeks out from under the dusty cloth. This is probably the facility for us to obtain more Commands. Railway models make one feel so nostalgic...

name: Rural Railway Model
description: An ordinary rural station, witness of the young ones' hopes and dreams that have been washed away by time. If one passes through the tunnel, will they find the life they have once longed for?

name: Railway Station Model
description: The industrial-era train station built with iron structures has replaced the previous ordinary station. The trains filled with mail and passengers have also been replaced by freight trains carrying raw materials. This is what they call technological progress.

name: Royal Railway Hub Model
description: After several upgrades, the Royal Railway Station Model has finally been completed. It is based on an important station in the capital of a certain pre-War empire that can only live on as a model.

name: Warehouse Model Foundation
description: We can build a warehouse model on this foundation to store the Commands shipped from HQ. Wondering how a model warehouse can store Fairy Commands? I'd like to know as well...

name: Temporary Warehouse Model
description: A temporary warehouse has been built, but this structure made out of fine wires and spray-painted plastic film is extremely fragile. Please exercise caution when retrieving Commands, Commander.

name: Industrial Warehouse Model
description: A warehouse built with red bricks and sheet metal is much more durable and can store more Commands. (This is not the story of Three Little Pigs!)

name: Advanced Warehouse Model
description: An advanced warehouse model that uses renewable energy and is environmentally friendly. The key is its geometric structural design. How else would it have won the Pritzker Architecture Prize?

name: Blank Weather System
description: Since there are hooks on the ceiling, building a realistic weather system here will likely make the Fairies happy, thus increasing their EXP gain. At the end of the day, maintaining a good vibe in the dark underground is of the utmost importance.

name: Cloudy Weather System
description: A small patch of dark clouds is the beginning of everything. Don't underestimate the model-making skills that go into creating miniature clouds out of cotton, glue, and spray paint.

name: Dark Moon Weather System
description: As the mysterious dark moon reveals its mottled edges from behind the clouds, the Fairies excitedly bring out their tarot cards and summoning candles. I hope they don't accidentally open a teleportation gateway to somewhere otherworldly...

name: Twin Moon Weather System
description: What's better than a Weather System with a moon? The answer is a Weather System with TWO moons! Moreover, they're shining brightly and are much prettier than the potato-like Mars moons, Phobos and Deimos.

name: Christmas Eve Banquet
description: A precious taken before the Christmas Eve banquet. Once the feast starts, neither the T-Dolls nor the food will be recognizable.

name: Weirder Things - Kitty Party
description: Halloween 2018's Special Commemorative Poster

name: Weirder Things - Spooky Kitty
description: Spooky Kitty's Nest

name: Weirder Things - Halloween Fright
description: Halloween 2018's Special Commemorative Poster

name: Fatal Performance - Black Sports Motorcycle
description: AEK999's beloved vehicle. Because she changes her attire before going out for a ride, only her close riding buddies know of the existence of this vehicle.

name: Honey Sweet Moment - Elite N.E.E.T. Sign
description: Another sign that reveals the true purpose of life. But is this "truth" reality?

name: Honey Sweet Moment - Wedding Curtains
description: Seeing the bouquets on the curtains reminds you of that sweet moment, even if it is filled with happiness that is not your own.

name: Steel Giant
description: A painting that looks as if it's world famous. It gives you a heavy feeling in your heart every time you look at it...

name: Gems Agent
description: Experienced agents will always don an identity before their mission. An exquisitely crafted calling card is also a symbol of professionalism.

name: Time Throne
description: There is no such thing as an eternal throne. Power is like fine sand; it will leak from your grasp bit by bit.

name: Fel in Diving Suit
description: To commemorate the adventures on the beach, Fel got a new outfit... Not sure when it's gonna come in useful, but FAL's happy about it, and that's what matters!

name: Ghost Trap, Counterattack!
description: Is this the biggest pinch that the Invincible No. 1 Netizen MDR has ever faced? Who could have done something so...amusing? (MDR: delete plz)

name: Witch's Forest Wallpaper
description: This picture was taken during a private Griffin Halloween party. That night...all the Dolls in the picture...changed back to their regular clothes.

name: Bionic Pig Charger
description: This bionic pig-shaped mobile charger can quickly charge T-Dolls and has many adaptors to handle various circumstances... "Adaptors? What do you mean by adaptors?" Gr MP5 asks.

name: Door Guardian Window Cutout
description: A paper cutout that Type95 made after witnessing the events of Chinese New Year Eve. "I won't have two dummies who froze themselves solid on Chinese New Year's Eve as my door guardians! Send them back to where they came from!" Type97 said after seeing it.

name: Magic Dressing Table
description: Sufficiently advanced science is indistinguishable from magic. No Doll can resist the magic that makes them beautiful, and so they sit here for long periods of time.

name: Sweet Selection
description: There is no luck in life, only individual choices. Of course, there are times when you don't want to choose... Then again, choosing everything is also a choice.

name: Tactical Stealth Box
description: The contemporary Romeo won't have to climb up a balcony to see Juliet. All he needs to do is put Juliet in this stealth box, and she can elope with him as safely and comfortably as if she were sitting on a train.

name: Operation Ball Girl
description: The girls look absolutely stunning on the stage. If there is always such a performance in every random gala, I'd look forward to it even if it is a total farce.

name: Custom Orange Kitty Lifeguard
description: A new model of orange lifeguard kitty equipped with cutting-edge gear reports for duty! But who can this frail little kitty save in the vast ocean? It can't even save itself.

name: Mermaid Stand
description: To soothe the disappointment of not seeing any mermaids, the Commander had this mermaid stand especially created for the T-Dolls. But T-Dolls with a big head should refrain from squeezing in too hard...

name: "Shall we play a game?"
description: "...Sis? Don't be afriad. There's so much I can do. I can protect you. I can even... Heheh, shall we play a game?"

name: Space Gentledog
description: "I. Super star dancer. Gold farming." "Kalina?! The dog translator you just bought really does work! ...Wait, no! Come and see what kind of scary stuff this dog translator just said!"

name: X'mas Sock Full of Presents
description: A modest-looking X'mas Sock that contains the well wishes and kindness of countless people - "Which makes this a perfectly safe place to hide," thinks a certain dinergate infiltrating Griffin. Hopefully it will deliver the presents successfully.

name: Vixen User Manual
description: A manual for "Vixen", a mech built especially for Christmas... Even though it can't soar through the sky, it can still deliver your presents! It's really hardworking!

name: Sticker of Good Fortune
description: A sticker that bears the Dolls' well-wishing. Someone stuck it on the Commander's door.

name: Space Chair
description: This is a miraculous chair. Just sit on it, relax, close your eyes and count to five, then everything will change...

name: Secret Recorder
description: Things that document the truth are never immediately visible. Guess how many camera heads there are in here?

name: "Standstill"
description: Though Death has brought me to a halt, please remember me by this... I have lived.

name: "Concept"
description: Please, please, please specify if it's a banquet or a party next time you promote an event. There's a huge difference in scale between the two.

name: Current - Command Center
description: The source of all battle commands. The Commander's main workplace.

name: Current - HQ Intelligence Center
description: The main intelligence center. A vault of Griffin's most valuable asset.

name: Current - HQ Data Room
description: The place where intelligence is screened and processed. Miss Kalina has spent most of her precious youth here.

name: Current - Special Reception
description: Entry to this mysterious little room is forbidden for Griffin Dolls, and it seems uninhabited, but every now and then footsteps can be heard from it in the middle of the night…

name: Current - Frontline Intelligence Center
description: A branch of the Frontline Combat Team - true elites understand the importance of intelligence.

name: Current - Frontline Basecamp
description: The basecamp of the Frontline Combat Team. The final stop before an operation begins.

name: Current - Frontline Depot
description: The depot of the Frontline Combat Team. Most of the things stored in here aren't meant for the public eye.

name: Current - Response Intelligence Center
description: A branch of the Response Combat Team - so much intel is gathered here it could work nine Kalinas to death.

name: Current - Response Basecamp
description: The basecamp of the Response Combat Team. The atmosphere isn't too cold and deadly here...in fact, it's quite laid-back.

name: Current - Response Depot
description: The depot of the Response Combat Team. Unimaginable things are stored here - because it literally has EVERYTHING.

name: Current - Border Intelligence Center
description: A branch of the Border Surveillance Corps - mainly specializing in producing topographical images and diagrams. Do you like maps?

name: Current - Border Basecamp
description: Forward Basecamp, where echoes can be heard - no matter where you are, we'll be right behind you.

name: Current - Border Depot
description: The depot of the Border Surveillance Corps. Holy crap, you guys are even messier than the Response Combat Team!

name: Current - Support Intelligence Center
description: A branch of the General Support Team - the branch we're most familiar with and the source of most intel missions.

name: Current - Fairy Chamber
description: I repeat - those are not toys! Don't make me say that again!

name: Current - Garage
description: A hangout for the HOCs. Probably the place that resembles a military camp the most…

name: Current - Protocol Control Center
description: We don't know much about this stuff… Perhaps our enemies have more insight.

name: Current - Special Training Ground
description: A new training ground especially built for the Assimilated Forces. They value their privacy.

name: Current - Isolated Testing Ground
description: "What, you want to come with us?"

name: Current - Specialized Factory
description: It isn't exactly special treatment… We just use different tech.

name: Current - Café
description: Everyone likes a drink after a mission, but sometimes someone else comes along to fill in for Miss Springfield. I just hope I never run into such occasions.

name: Current - Dormitory
description: "Commander… No more than three. We can't take care of any more."

name: Current - Repair Bay
description: "Don't look at me! They said no more than three!"

name: Current - Cafeteria
description: The most human-like feature of Tactical Dolls is that they never let good food go to waste - though the list of Dolls banned from the kitchen is getting longer and longer.

name: Current - Supply Warehouse
description: This is Griffin's largest as well as tidiest warehouse, managed by Miss Kalina herself.

name: Current - Secretary Office
description: Miss Kalina's private office - What? So the Data Room isn't her office?

name: Current - Banquet Hall
description: A big hall reserved for large-scale events. Several Dolls also hang out here in their free time - but no drinking competitions!

name: Current - Club Activity Room
description: Dolls find leisure and entertainment here, but you can always see a few familiar faces in this room - "MDR, you're slacking off again!"
